1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala Isus i Marija, dragi naši, želim vas sve pozdraviti iz vječnog grada, iz Rima.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Danas sam ovdje sa mojom današnjom sugovornicom, sa sestrom Celinom.

3
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Njena životna priča počinje u Bosansko-Grahovu, u malome mjestu u jugozapadnoj Bosni.

4
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Njeno djetinstvo prekinuto je početkom drugog svjetskog rata i sukupom koji se događao na tim prostorima.

5
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Njenu cijelu životnu priču vam želimo danas donijeti. Pozivamo vas da poslušate ovaj intervju.

6
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sestro Celino, Hvala Isusi Marija, lijepom pozdrav. Hvala.

7
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam što ste pristali biti u intervju danas.

8
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vama da ste došli i da imate interes za to.

9
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu hvala.

10
00:00:53,000 --> 00:01:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Htio bih započeti sa vašim djetinstvom. Već sam spomenuo da ste živjeli, da ste rođeni u Bosanskom Grahovu.

11
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možete nam opisati kako su izgledale prve godine vašeg života? Vaša obitelj, samo vaše selo, naselje?

12
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ja sam sedmo djete u obitelji. Moja majka imala devetro djece. Troje je umrlo nakon par mjeseci. Tada su bile dječje bolestni kojima nije bilo lijeka.

13
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je nas bilo šestero koje nas ostale u životu. Ja sam bila tada najmlađa. Bila sam možda malo mezimica. Svi su me voljeli.

14
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mnogo puta sam bila kapricasta. Ali mama me znala dobro poučiti koji puta lijepim riječima, a koji puta i kapim šibom.

15
00:01:55,000 --> 00:02:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, kao sve majke koje su tada imale način. Svakako ja sam zadovoljna sa svojom obitelji.

16
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj otac je bio kovač, puno je radio, bio pošten čovjek. Svega su ga poznavali cijela okolica Grahovska, praoslavci i katolici.

17
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] I bili smo u slozi s tim, sa svim ljudima. Nije bilo među nama svađe, među katolicima i hrvatima.

18
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Katolicima hrvatima i praoslavcima, dakle srbima. Bili smo u slozi. Svak je živio u svojoj obitelji.

19
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi su se većinom bavili ratarstvom. Imali su recimo rovčarstvo, imali su blago. Bavili su se svojim obiteljima. Mirno su radili. Suradživali su dosta.

20
00:02:54,000 --> 00:03:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, bilo je miran život koji se može reći za jedno selo. Koje je bilo malo selo. Dakle, bilo je veliki obljaj. To je bilo selo gdje sam ja rođena.

21
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] I mali obljaj gdje su bili manjinima Hrvata i manjinima Sarića. Većinoma u našem selu, gdje sam se ja rodila, su bili skoro svi Sarići. Bila je samo jedna obitelja.

22
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] I jedna, mislim, bila je Manjić. Drugo su bili svi Sarići. I bile smo više, a manje povezani jer je to, dakle, to naselje postale od tri brata koje su došli iz Dalmacije.

23
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] I oni su se razdijelili i radili. I svaki je imao svoje obitelji. Jedno ga su nazvali Špiran i nastalo je Špiranovići. Tako da smo imali selo Špiranovići, a potječo je iz Sarića.

24
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] U mojem selju bilo je, dakle, ljudi su imali svaku svoju kuću, svoje obitelji, svoje njive, svoje krave, svoje ovce. I time su se bavili.

25
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Neko su ipak išli izvan Grahova, izvan svoga sela i radili su po željeznicama u drugim krajevima.

26
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je bilo dosta željezničara i u Krinu, i u Drvaru, i drugim gradovima koje ja nisam poznavala tada.

27
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je Hrvati su bili dosta imućni i mnogo više nego pravoslavci, ali bili su jako radišni. I ko radi, taj ima, ko ne radi, taj nema. I onda ide krasti i baviti se drugim poslovima.

28
00:04:49,000 --> 00:05:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, u mojem selu ja sam bila do devet godina, ali zadnje godine sam više, dakle, razmatrala kako je se zbivalo.

29
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na večer, recimo, bili su ljudi, molili su. Zvonilo je crkveno zvono, a mi smo bili uz crkveno zvono, baš nekoliko metara od crkve.

30
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kad bi zazvonilo crkveno zvono, tada bi ljudi počeli moliti Zdravu Mariju ili Anđelu Gospodnji. I svi su molili. Katolici su svi molili.

31
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] I za toga, onda bi ljudi večerali u svojim obiteljima, a dečki i djevojke, oni bi išli na prelose, zvalo.

32
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, su se susretrali u jednoj kući i tamo bi razgovarali pričaj i, dakle, razonodili se, recimo.

33
00:05:50,000 --> 00:06:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mnogi bi iz drugih sela pjevali, osobito muškarci, tako da se njihove pjesma su se čule iz jednog sela u drugi.

34
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to je se meni jako sviđalo. Ja sam volila več pjesmu, volila sam isto muziku, jer moj otac je svirao tamburicu.

35
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tako da smo mi u obitelji več bili naučili na muziku. Imao je isto i gusle.

36
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] A gusle su obično je svirao kad su pjevali epijske pjesme. A tada su najbolje pripoznavali Marka Kraljevića, Miloša Obilića i, dakle, rat na Kostovu polju.

37
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bitka na Kostovu polju. To su opjevavali. Tako je druga galda nisu imali. A i o Kulinu banu.

38
00:06:47,000 --> 00:07:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer, kaže, najbolji ban koji je bio u Bosni je bio Kulin ban. Tamo je bilo svega i svašta obitelj, obilnog svega bogatstva i mira.

39
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako to se ja sjećam. A inače, poslije, kako bi rekla, ja sam počela osnovnu školu, 39. godine, u prvom razredu.

40
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] I mi smo u školi uvijek počeli razred, če, kako se kaže... Nastavu.

41
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nastavu smo počeli s molitvom. Molili smo jednu molitvu koju ja i danas znam.

42
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako hoćete, ja ću vam izmoliti. Može, može da paći.

43
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] O moj Bože dragi, malim ti se molim. Pouči me tako da sve ljude volim. Dok sam još ovako u danima mladim, od jutra do mraka da veselo radim.

44
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da naučim nauk što za život treba. Da umenjem služit svakdenega hljeba. To je bio završetak.

45
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] I svak se prekrstio na svoj način. I tada smo nastavili. Dakle, učiteljica je nastavila svoju nastavu.

46
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo prvi razred. Nažalost, drugi razred nismo do konca završili jer je nastao rat.

47
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Već, mislim, u trećem mjesecu smo već vreknili školu jer je nastao rat četrdeseti prve.

48
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tako da ja drugi razred nisam potpuno završila, a koji sam poslije nastavila u požegi kad smo...

49
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sam izgubila cijelu godinu škole jer, nažalost, tako je bilo.

50
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako vrijeme. Tako vrijeme. To je prvo ratno.

51
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mis među nas i praoslavaca bila je sloga. Moj otac je imao mnogo prijatelja praoslavaca.

52
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] I čak je s jednim bio povratim. On bi dolazio k nama recimo za Božić i bio je naš gost.

53
00:08:58,000 --> 00:09:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kod nas bi ostao i spavao bi kod nas. A moj otac je išao na njegovu krsnu slavu.

54
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je bilo tu, mislim, veliko prijateljstvo.

55
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da oni su nas kad je bio napad, onda su oni nas i spasili, ti ljudi koji su bili s nama veliki prijatelji.

56
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da. Znači u samom Grahovu prije rata, prije sukoba, bio je lijep suživot između katolika i praoslavica.

57
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako lijepo. Recimo bi u samom središnju grada, moj otac imao jednog trgovca, praoslavca.

58
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] On bi, recimo kad bi ja izišla iz škole, ako bi prešno mami trebalo, recimo šečera, kave i sl.

59
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam to već u prvom razredu išla bi kod duća, mi bi rekli, i uzela bi i moj tata bi poslije se to platio.

60
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je bilo to takav povezanost i to je bi za nas normalno bilo.

61
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da bi smo kaženi, a eto, u školi smo, imali smo lijepu školu, imali smo dom Gavrila Principa.

62
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Beata Gavrila Principa, to je naš susjed. Dakle, obiljaju prva kuća, došavši iz grada, je njegova kuća od Gavrila Principa.

63
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mi smo o tom puno razgovarali, mi Hrvati. Znam da je on to učinio, nažalost to je bio jedan delikt, ali da možemo, tako je bilo.

64
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, taj dio oko prvog svjetskog grata nije ostavio previše utiska na vama.

65
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, nije, makar u Grahovu. U Grahovu, dakle, bio je njegov dom i tamo bi nije imali priredbe.

66
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koji put bi bila priredba i mi djeca smo išli na tu priredbu. Ja se sjećam, ja sam bila jako znatiželjna.

67
00:10:58,000 --> 00:11:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] I u gradu bi je bio isto njihova crkva. Ja se sjećam da idem u njihovu crkvu da vidim.

68
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene sve zanimalo.

69
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan dan sam unišla u crkvu.

70
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bila je njihova obred i njihovi su bili.

71
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vidila sam svi ljudi stoje i svi s rukama prekri ženovka.

72
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene bilo to čudno. Svi stoje dok mi u crkvi smo uvili s ruke sklopljene, i muške i ženke.

73
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja to rekla župniku. Pa kažem kako to. I onda ja sam pobjegla jer oni su imali ove velike slike.

74
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Za mene su bili prevelike one oči i sve. Ja sam pobjegla jer sam se bojala.

75
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uplašili ste.

76
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se preslašla iz letna iz crkve.

77
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] I rekla ja to u župniku.

78
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem veličasni joj ja sam da kažem bila. On je mene izdružio da nikad nisi više išla. Pa da je se smjelo tada.

79
00:11:57,000 --> 00:12:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] A šta sam ja znala je djeto.

80
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dijete.

81
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam. Idemo. Željno, hoću da vidi.

82
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] E tako da. Ali nismo imali recimo kakvire sporova između njih toga. Izmeru vjere. Poštivali smo se.

83
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Među Hrvatima smo se pozdravljali hvala Nisus, a ima smo rekli dobar dan.

84
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tako da oni su znali da mi Hrvati se pozdravljamo tako, a njima smo tako. Oni su se između sebe.

85
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da nije bilo, mislim, dužve i sporova između nas.

86
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] A kog je bilo više? Pravoslavnaca?

87
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pravoslavnaca je tada prije rata 11.000. Nas Hrvata oko 1000 je bilo. Zato smo mi bili manjina i morali smo uvijek šutiti.

88
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da. Ali bilo je mješanih brakova, kumstava međuseljih?

89
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije, bio je koji put mješanih brakova.

90
00:12:52,000 --> 00:13:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, iz našeg, u našem selu, baš li je sestra od najbogatijeg srbe, pravoslavca, udata bila za jednog Hrvata, katolika.

91
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] I taj čovjek je jako bio pošten. Mi smo ali vrlo pošteni ljudi pravoslavaca u selu.

92
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ja se ne mogu... Jedino je bio jedan siromak koji nije bio pri pameti, ali...

93
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, to je.

94
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moja mama bumešla: "Pazi, zahvali Bogu da imaš zdravu pamet."

95
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] To nemojamo se nikad smijati ili nešto izdrukivati nekomu to.

96
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Inače bili su normalni ljudi. Uz razredi smo bili jednaki.

97
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije bilo sporova nikad u razligu.

98
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo, kad se trebalo naš vjeronauk,

99
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda smo mi išli u jedan razred. Svi skupa.

100
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, svi katolici i župnik došao imati nama vjeronauku.

101
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da oni su imali posebno.

102
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da bilo tu jedno poštivanje, recimo.

103
00:13:58,000 --> 00:14:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se ne mogu, da nema nikakve sporova ni s kim nismo imali.

104
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jako su učiteljice bile s većina pravoslavke.

105
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači pravoslavke su bili učiteljice?

106
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pravoslavke. Moja učiteljica je bila pravoslavka.

107
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesu vam pravili problema katolici?

108
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, nikako. Ja u prvom razredu sam bila odličan džak.

109
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači bili su svi pravedni?

110
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pravedno je bilo.

111
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ja sam imala sve odlično tada.

112
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sjećam se jedan dan.

113
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nekoji nisu napravili zadaće.

114
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sve u reštu.

115
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve u zatvor.

116
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, morali su ostati.

117
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Rekli su u reštu.

118
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam na šta reštu.

119
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] U zatvor.

120
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ostali su svi.

121
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, nisu išli kući.

122
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve do poslje poodne.

123
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja bilo svem, niko, svi kar.

124
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam, pa ja ću isto ostati.

125
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, društvo druge.

126
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedino, ja sam trebala ići kuće.

127
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa šta ću ja ići sama?

128
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ću isto ostati.

129
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:02,000
[UNKNOWN] Pa.

130
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako.

131
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ivaljda nisu napravili zadaće.

132
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se ne siđam šta je bilo.

133
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Takako ja sam bila oslobođena.

134
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Drugi, svi su i praoslavci i katolici.

135
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svi u reštu.

136
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi su završili zatvor.

137
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači.

138
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imali ste po ovome što ste sad rekli,

139
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] jako lijepo djetinstvo sve do '41.

140
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

141
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam jela mirno djetinstvo, mislim.

142
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Posebno recimo moja sestra jedna se udala

143
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam ja imala četiri godine.

144
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] A druga je, aha, to moram spomenuti.

145
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tada obično kad je mladić,

146
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] dakle od sestre,

147
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] on je meni dao novac 50 dinara, srebranih dinara.

148
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mom bratu nekoliko kuna.

149
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nekoliko, mislim, kako je rekla, centa.

150
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad moj brat Marko vidio je,

151
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] on je bio stariji od mene pet godina.

152
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad on meni kaže, znaš šta?

153
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ću tebi dat dva,

154
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] a ti meni daj jedan.

155
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa dobro.

156
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mi dao 50 dinara srebranih,

157
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji su vrlo vrijedili tada.

158
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je meni dao od dva dinara.

159
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] A bio je stariji.

160
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Stariji od mene.

161
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mama je gledala to.

162
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Marko, kako si lopo, kako je varaš.

163
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mama je štitila vas.

164
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da.

165
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta ja mislim, šta mene briga.

166
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan, ja imam dva dinara.

167
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

168
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam znala vrijednosti novca.

169
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je tako bilo.

170
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] To se sjećam.

171
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] I s bratom Markom,

172
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] najviše smo nas dvoje igrali.

173
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Lijepo mi je bilo se sjećanje po zimi.

174
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Recimo, mi smo po zimi.

175
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je snijeg.

176
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Malo se je radilo okolo.

177
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda bi mi igrali se.

178
00:16:57,000 --> 00:17:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tata, i strici, oba dva brata i ja.

179
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili bi skrivali prste.

180
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bi skupila sve kape i stabila na stol.

181
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda bi mi skrivali.

182
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kad bi ja išla žmiriti da pogodim gdje je prsten,

183
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] i onda ja...

184
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovek bi gledala strica.

185
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] A strica je mene jako volio.

186
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] On bi samo mene namignuo.

187
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ja bi pogodila gdje je.

188
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] A brat Marko, ne, ne vrijedi, kaže.

189
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Strica je namiguo.

190
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo mi igrali šaleci.

191
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Inače, nas dvoje smo dosta igrali.

192
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Igrali smo posle i šaha.

193
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam naučila je vrlo mala igrali šah s bratom Markom.

194
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo mi znali, posebno kad smo bili malo veći.

195
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam već bila deset godina.

196
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda bi znali po cijele saate sjediti sa jednom partijom.

197
00:17:56,000 --> 00:18:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znali, on je bi odličan.

198
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali on bi mene uvijek nešto bi napravio da ja se restresem i da oprimo još skakomato.

199
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je tako bilo.

200
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znao je kako isprovocirati.

201
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, on je dobro igralo.

202
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja još danas se sjećam te igre.

203
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Igrali smo.

204
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako imali smo lijepu obitelj, recimo.

205
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda sa Božića, recimo, i za badnje večeri.

206
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer bismo bili blizu crkve, išli smo svi na svetu misu, na badnjak.

207
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kod bi se vratili, onda bi jeli.

208
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali prije jela molili smo.

209
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda bi se svi izljubili.

210
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mir Boženje.

211
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bili smo svi na svetoj misi.

212
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad onda počeli bi na tata i mama, stricu, onda mi djeco stavali.

213
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to je meni se jako sviđalo.

214
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, ta ljubav, obitelji.

215
00:18:58,000 --> 00:19:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svi smo, dakle, bili na svetoj misi.

216
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Izmolili smo, Bog je s nama.

217
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to mi se isto sviđalo.

218
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] To se dobro sjeća.

219
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Miž Božene se rekla.

220
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mir Boži.

221
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mil Boži.

222
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] I poljubili bi tatu, mamu, strica, brata, sestri.

223
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tako.

224
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Urazilo vam se u pamćenju?

225
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je.

226
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možda sam za ja to bila, ja sam dosta bila nježna kao djevojčica.

227
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možda baš zato jer sam imala te, dakle, te velike pozornosti sa strane mojih.

228
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je to meni ostalo.

229
00:19:36,000 --> 00:19:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Puno ljubavi ste primila.

230
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Puno ljubavi.

231
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam dobila puno ljubavi.

232
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zato kažem hvala Bogu.

233
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek mi je žao kad čujem da koja osoba ne ima mame ili nema tate.

234
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je jako žalosno.

235
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer, mamu trebaš imati tatu.

236
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tata ti daje energiju.

237
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tate, dakle, snagu.

238
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mama ti daje ljubav.

239
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tata ti daje sigurnost.

240
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da si siguran.

241
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mama ti daje onu nježnost koju trebaš imati.

242
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sam ja dožijela.

243
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj otac mene jako volio.

244
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bi koji put došla njemu u njegovu radionicu.

245
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda imao je knjigu gdje je zapisivo ko kada dolazi svaki dan.

246
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je meni rekao, kad sam ja počela prvi razred, onda ja sam došla da vidim kako tata radi.

247
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] On kaže: "Znaš šta, kad ti stvršiš školu ti ćeš biti meni tajnica.

248
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti ćeš meni sve zapisivati."

249
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to je meni dalo važnost, veliko važnost.

250
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ću tajnica vidi tata.

251
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] To su tako moja djetinstva.

252
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to djetinstvo je u stvari naglo prekinuto.

253
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naglo je prekinuta, kad je navijestio se rat.

254
00:20:57,000 --> 00:20:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] 1941.

255
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je vojska nagrnila u Grahovo.

256
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Raspustila se vojska u cijeloj Jugoslaviji.

257
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] I Grahovo je puno vojske bilo.

258
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] A naši su se muškarci sakrivali.

259
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam pjela zašto?

260
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer je bila proglašena nezavisna drlava Hrvatska.

261
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sada Srbi su se digli.

262
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta je sada?

263
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvati su dobili svoju nezavisnost.

264
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to je...

265
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je meni...

266
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] U strahu smo bili.

267
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ne znam kako se ta vojska je raspršila.

268
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne pamtim.

269
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda tek u šest sedmom mjesecu

270
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] je nastala ta napad na Grahovo.

271
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naši su tada isto organizirali se vojsku.

272
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, došli su iz drugih gradova

273
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] da su organizirali vojsku, domobrane i naše ljude.

274
00:21:58,000 --> 00:22:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da su nekoj bili...

275
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Malo ih je išlo, mislim. Vrlo malo je.

276
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo nas je malo, mislim, ljudi.

277
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Malo mi je.

278
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tesuću ljudište.

279
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, jedna Šaka Hrvata.

280
00:22:09,000 --> 00:22:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali neki su joj otišli u visku.

281
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj brat nije išao jer je mu bio mlad.

282
00:22:13,000 --> 00:22:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imao joj tek sedamnest godina.

283
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] A neki su...

284
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda su...

285
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad su oni napali,

286
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvati dobili su slobodnu državu,

287
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda to nije išlo pod kapu.

288
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda su napadali sela.

289
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad su naše selo napali,

290
00:22:33,000 --> 00:22:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] s brda sa brda,

291
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] puštali su dozgo, sigurno narod je...

292
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ujutro rano,

293
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] sjećam se ujutro rano,

294
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] došli su zvati da se ljudi organiziraju.

295
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da će biti napad na Grahovo.

296
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda svi muškarci su išli u središte grada,

297
00:22:55,000 --> 00:22:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] da su tamo...

298
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali oružja nisu,

299
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali malo oružja.

300
00:22:58,000 --> 00:23:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj brat je imao neku pušku,

301
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] a nije znao niti manevrirati,

302
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] pa je dao drugome...

303
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako dao...

304
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je bio inače mirne naravi.

305
00:23:08,000 --> 00:23:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] On nije bio za vojsku.

306
00:23:10,000 --> 00:23:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da...

307
00:23:12,000 --> 00:23:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mnogi su onda pobjegli,

308
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] nisu se mogli obraniti.

309
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu se mogli obraniti,

310
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] nemaju oružja.

311
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi pobjegli.

312
00:23:18,000 --> 00:23:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mnoge žene se pobjegle s djecom

313
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] i mogli muškarci.

314
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Skoro svi su izbjegli.

315
00:23:24,000 --> 00:23:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ostao je u središte samo moj tata

316
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] i još jedan starac.

317
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Od čim su ušli u naše servo,

318
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] streljali ga na cesti.

319
00:23:34,000 --> 00:23:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da nije bilo muškaraca uopće.

320
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] A taj napad...

321
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko je izveo?

322
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer u uđbenicima se često spomenje

323
00:23:43,000 --> 00:23:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] da su to partizani?

324
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] To su došli.

325
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] No, no, to su bili četnici.

326
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Srbi su organizirali čete.

327
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, svi oni koji su bili u vojsci

328
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] u Jugoslavenskoj

329
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] i onda neko su pokupili isto iz sela.

330
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Organizirali su se.

331
00:24:01,000 --> 00:24:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su imali svakog

332
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] i oružja, i motika, i srpova.

333
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svakog oružja recimo.

334
00:24:09,000 --> 00:24:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo da napadnu ljude.

335
00:24:11,000 --> 00:24:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to je organizirao

336
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne iz našeg sela niko,

337
00:24:15,000 --> 00:24:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] nego iz drugih krajeva

338
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] ko neki momčilo...

339
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se zva on?

340
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam mu pisala u svoje dom...

341
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, Pop Dukić.

342
00:24:26,000 --> 00:24:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pop Dukić.

343
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pop Dukić.

344
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dujić.

345
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Momčilo Dujić.

346
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] I momčilo je...

347
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Drugo ima Mučilo.

348
00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad sam zaboravila mu prezime.

349
00:24:35,000 --> 00:24:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam to zapisala,

350
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] prije sam znala,

351
00:24:38,000 --> 00:24:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] sad sam već zaboravila.

352
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, oni su bili glavni pokretači

353
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] te organizacije

354
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] i onda ljusi prihvatili su ljudi

355
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] iz drugih sela

356
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] napali su na nas Sariće.

357
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Najprije na male Sariće.

358
00:24:56,000 --> 00:24:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda na nas...

359
00:24:58,000 --> 00:25:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da su mnoge ljude

360
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji su bili u malom Sariću,

361
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] nekoj koji su ostali,

362
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] jako su ih mučili.

363
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, nekima su sve zupe povadili.

364
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da,

365
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] kada smo mi prošli kod to,

366
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo bili,

367
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] ostali smo mi kod kuća

368
00:25:15,000 --> 00:25:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] i sad smo čekali šta?

369
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da dođe tata.

370
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tata se nije vraćao iz grada.

371
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nismo znali šta što ćemo činiti.

372
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda mama kaže:

373
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Idemo prema malim Sarićima,

374
00:25:25,000 --> 00:25:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] pa ćemo s njima odrediti šta ćemo napraviti."

375
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi tamo prošli,

376
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] kada tamo oni već,

377
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] štetnici već u njihovom selu sve zauzeli.

378
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kad su videli nas da idemo iz velike Sarića,

379
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] oni, pa rekla nama s puškama.

380
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Započeli pucat.

381
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda brat Marko i ja,

382
00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo bili mlađi,

383
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] pobjegli smo u neko žito.

384
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moja šetra mojka je kuruze,

385
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] a Ivica je ostao zadnji,

386
00:25:53,000 --> 00:25:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] brat moj koji je imao sedamnaest godina.

387
00:25:55,000 --> 00:25:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je imao težak kaput,

388
00:25:57,000 --> 00:25:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer mama je rekla:

389
00:25:58,000 --> 00:26:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Uzmi kaput jer možda ćemo ostati vani,

390
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne znamo škako će biti vrijeme."

391
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] i njega su odmah uhvatili.

392
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mama kad je videla njega uhvatili,

393
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] počeli ga tući.

394
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Mama, k njima šta je?"

395
00:26:09,000 --> 00:26:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Po sreći poznala je jednog našog poznanca,

396
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji je iz drugog sela, Pravoslavca.

397
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Pa kume?"

398
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Pa kume, to je moj sin!"

399
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Aa, kovačica!"

400
00:26:23,000 --> 00:26:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moji mali uznali kovačica.

401
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Aa, kovačica!"

402
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda kaže:

403
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Prestanjete tako da ga nisu više tukli."

404
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odmah su ga počeli tući.

405
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] S lijeva, s desna.

406
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] A moj brat je kao ovčica.

407
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] I vidio, jako mirne naravi.

408
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] I po sreći.

409
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] A sestra je tamo,

410
00:26:42,000 --> 00:26:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] nje su doveli iz nekoj kuruze,

411
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] tako da nam je rekla:

412
00:26:46,000 --> 00:26:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Pa tvoje moja piće."

413
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo nas dvoje smo čekali šta se događa.

414
00:26:51,000 --> 00:26:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže:

415
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Marko, ja imam pištolju džepu."

416
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Aa, šta ćemo sada?"

417
00:26:58,000 --> 00:27:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] E, kažem:

418
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] "I sad mi nećemo ići jer oni ima pištolju džepu."

419
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ga pregledaju, nećemo pištolju, gotovo si.

420
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] E, kaže:

421
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] "I mi zovemo da mama dođe k nama, da se mi bojimo,

422
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] neka dođe k nama."

423
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] I mama došla k nama, onda mama je rekao:

424
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Marko, mama, ja imam pištolju, a moj sin ko kacušli."

425
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, onda ga bio je neki plast blizu,

426
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda je gurnuo ga u plast, tako da smo došli svojima.

427
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je mama zamolila,

428
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] taj kum, toga mama zvala, onda je rekao:

429
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Slušaj, ne mojte se vraćati kući, jer naleti će druga rulja i pogubit će vas, jer ne poznaju vas."

430
00:27:41,000 --> 00:27:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ja ću vas poslati u pravoslavno selo,

431
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] i tamo smo imeli tog kuma od tate."

432
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tata mu je bio kumpaljda na vjenčanju.

433
00:27:52,000 --> 00:27:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže:

434
00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Idite k njemu, tamo će vam, bit će vam sigurnije, on vas pozna, tamo vas poznaju."

435
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo mi išli tamo, ali smo susreli svašta na putu.

436
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa neki sa puškama, neki sa banetama, neki sa motikama, neki sa vilama, pa to je tako.

437
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali pošto mama buje pismeno.

438
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedima kad smo došli, skoro već se vidilo selo na jednom visaravan,

439
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] da je leti neki na bijelom konju s pištoljem, jedan veliki pištolj:

440
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Stojte da na hrvatsku majku, kada ste, sada sada idete."

441
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mama kaže: "Idemo u tome i tome i valizmi, u našem kumu i tako."

442
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] I pokazali mu: "Neće da čuje, ja ću vas sada sve, jednu podru."

443
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ruke u zraku.

444
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da ja sam uz mamu bila, držala sam za njenu suknu,

445
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] ruku se nalogravi i sad sam gledala koga će prvog pogoditi.

446
00:28:57,000 --> 00:29:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mama kaže: "Djeco, molimo o vjerovanjem."

447
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mama je rekao: "Ako nam sada, Bog neka bude s nama."

448
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Brat nama je bio naš susjed, Ivan, i oni mole o vjerovanjem.

449
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moje sve treba i biće Isuse milosrđa.

450
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja nešta, ja gledam samo i kažem: "Bože, samo dan života."

451
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam morala.

452
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo rekla: "Bože, samo dan života."

453
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda sam mislila: "Ako danas se spasiš, naš ćeš uvijek zauvijek spasiti."

454
00:29:33,000 --> 00:29:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ako nas danas spasiš, bit ćemo zauvijek spašeni.

455
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko ste godina tada imali?

456
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Devet imali.

457
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Devet godina.

458
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Devet godina sam gledala.

459
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, ja nisam molila.

460
00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam samo rekla: "Boga, oca, sam molila da mi dadne dan života."

461
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kakav još će je bio iznutra?

462
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste bili u velikom strahu?

463
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam se toliko bojala.

464
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo sam se bojala da će mi pio prije pogoditi mamo.

465
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je onda ja gotov si.

466
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ti mamo...

467
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni mene ostave samo.

468
00:30:03,000 --> 00:30:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pogupujem braću.

469
00:30:05,000 --> 00:30:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kući ja sama.

470
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je samo mene bio uvijek strah.

471
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da ja ostanem sama.

472
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Isto tako u Poželji, kad su Partizani u Poželji.

473
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se uvijek bojala.

474
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ubiće tatu, strica, mamo.

475
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene će ostaviti samo.

476
00:30:20,000 --> 00:30:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na samoća sam se ja bojala.

477
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je strahovito da ostaneš bez ikoga.

478
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to je...

479
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sigurno je normalno za jedno dijelo.

480
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koje je navezano na roditelji.

481
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

482
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Još je malo...

483
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bili ste mali tatu.

484
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Devet godina.

485
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Devet godina.

486
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Trebaš još mamu, drebaš oca.

487
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da to je stvarno bilo.

488
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali hvala Bogu.

489
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Opet je uzeo list, pročitao.

490
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idite, vidjet ćemo se brzo.

491
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tako smo došli u to selo.

492
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prihvatili nas ljudi jako su bili s nama prijazni stvarno.

493
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] S njima smo večerali.

494
00:30:59,000 --> 00:31:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda smo morali bježati i sve selo njihovo.

495
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer se bojali su se Njemaca.

496
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da će doći Njemci.

497
00:31:07,000 --> 00:31:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da će njih pokosit.

498
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad smo išli s njima u šumu.

499
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] U brdo.

500
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] U brdo.

501
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tamo smo prosporili neke deke.

502
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da smo ležali pod vedrem nebom.

503
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam odmah zaspala jer vidi se da sam bila umorna od svega.

504
00:31:24,000 --> 00:31:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Između mame i sestre.

505
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna donaga od doba noći.

506
00:31:29,000 --> 00:31:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] mama šapče sestri Naci.

507
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže sestra smo je zvali Stanislava, a zvali smo je Nacor.

508
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naci kaže: Nacor gore, kolita, korita gore.

509
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Od nebo užarenog.

510
00:31:46,000 --> 00:31:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve.

511
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ona je bila rođena u koritima, zato je znala.

512
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, gdje su korita.

513
00:31:54,000 --> 00:31:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je manjčino rodno selo.

514
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Rodno selo mamino.

515
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve.

516
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo tako...

517
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Cijelo nebo je tamo bilo.

518
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo vatra.

519
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga i kod naše kuće.

520
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Plamen.

521
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ogroman plamen.

522
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Između crkve i naše kuće.

523
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naša kuća je bila iz kamena.

524
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne mogla goriti.

525
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kamena kuća, kuća je gori.

526
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali gori.

527
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda znači, ovdje je župna crkva ili župna kuća.

528
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali bio je neki plast i taj su plast zapalili.

529
00:32:31,000 --> 00:32:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo mi...

530
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sutra dan kad smo se probudili, onda sišli smo.

531
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije bilo ne traga Njemaca.

532
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, sišli smo, s njima smo doručkovali.

533
00:32:42,000 --> 00:32:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je mama rekla:

534
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ja se s djecom vraćam kući, pa šta Bog da?"

535
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali on je savjetovao mami da ostane Ivica i ovaj Ivan.

536
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da njih boje ostanu, da je ipak za njih opasno.

537
00:32:57,000 --> 00:32:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Muškarci.

538
00:32:58,000 --> 00:32:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Muškarci su.

539
00:32:59,000 --> 00:33:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da mama i nas troje došli smo kući i baš na vratima župna kuće, pa tata ide s jednim prijateljem praoslavcom.

540
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Iđu pokupiti ove posude koje su bile za posljednje pomasti, za krizmu.

541
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to su oni se razbacali, znaš.

542
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je tata to skupio lijepo i doneso u našu kuću.

543
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mama je to stavila jednu veliku korpu i to smo mi pokrili.

544
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo sačuvali to.

545
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je bilo sve u srebro i zlato i tako.

546
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo, kad su došli italijani, onda smo to predali kapelanu italijanskom.

547
00:33:46,000 --> 00:33:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da se to spasilo.

548
00:33:48,000 --> 00:33:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to su pregledali.

549
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan smo imali pregled kad su došli u četnicu.

550
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan.

551
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da...

552
00:33:55,000 --> 00:34:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Eto, onda kad smo se mi vratili kući, tata je došao, rekao da je njegov vrat Stric naš, on je pobjegao za knin.

553
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sada nismo znali drugi kako su savršili.

554
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] A četnici svaki dan su dolazili u našu kuću.

555
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Htjeli su pušku od brata.

556
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Neko im je dao da je brat moj imao pušku.

557
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mama je rekla: "On je imao pušku, a on ne zna s puškom ravnati."

558
00:34:27,000 --> 00:34:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže: "On je toliko blage naravi, da on nije za pušku."

559
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to je bilo dnevno.

560
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] A brat Marko i ja bih stajali na balkonu, naša kuća imala mali balkončinj, mi bih stajali na balkonu da vidimo kako će.

561
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako će stvar završiti.

562
00:34:46,000 --> 00:34:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mama bi uvijek išla za njima.

563
00:34:48,000 --> 00:34:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ubite prije mene, onda njega.

564
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je pravedan, on nema puške, on nema.

565
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] I jedva smo se riješili toga.

566
00:34:57,000 --> 00:34:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ga nisu više progonili.

567
00:34:59,000 --> 00:35:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] A bilo je to skoro jedan dana, to svaki dan.

568
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Brat je bio u stoni, on je bio blag kao ovočica stvarno.

569
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ibica je bio najbolji u obitelji.

570
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali njega?

571
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] E, dobro.

572
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo se mi riješili.

573
00:35:16,000 --> 00:35:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali nismo zadnje vrijeme dolazila bi čerka od tog po bratima od moga oca.

574
00:35:24,000 --> 00:35:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] I rekla bi nam, mame bi došla reći:

575
00:35:26,000 --> 00:35:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sakrivajte djecu.

576
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nemojte da djeca budu u kući.

577
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ako navale, najprije će djecu zatamaniti.

578
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tato neće jer njega trebaju.

579
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je bio kovač, jedini kovač u cijeloj pokolici.

580
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] I njega su trebali.

581
00:35:44,000 --> 00:35:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, onda mi mi spavali jedan put u polju,

582
00:35:47,000 --> 00:35:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] među krompirima, nekada među odahle.

583
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan put smo u jednom brdu.

584
00:35:57,000 --> 00:36:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na brdašću imali smo jednu bašću sa kupusom.

585
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Velike glavice kupusa.

586
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo izmiju tikvi ležali.

587
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mogli smo imati zmije, smo mogli doći.

588
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa nam se ne dogodilo.

589
00:36:09,000 --> 00:36:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nekad smo se zakopali u sjenu.

590
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo glavu smo imali oni.

591
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa posvuda smo spavali.

592
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo, kažem, grozno.

593
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je trojela do 8. septembra.

594
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedno je nedjelje.

595
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bila je prva nedjelja.

596
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] velika povorka.

597
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pred njima je jedan konjanik sa bajonetom u ruci.

598
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] I za njim ovi svi puni puške na puškama bajonete.

599
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idu prema našem selu.

600
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] od grahovi.

601
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vi ste vidili kako je to blizu.

602
00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je male, jedno, dva kilometra koje ne više.

603
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idu prema nama.

604
00:36:58,000 --> 00:37:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mi svi na ulici, izvan kuća, gledamo šta je, šta će sada biti.

605
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] A oni idu da nas pokolju.

606
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni bi nas svi našli pred kućom.

607
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve bi nas poklali.

608
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako to da ni išlo?

609
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] I taj jedan put, iza njih leti jedan na konju.

610
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] I zaustali ih.

611
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] I oni se okrenuše.

612
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta je?

613
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je jedan pametan pravoslavac.

614
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Rekao je:

615
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ljudi, pa šta ćete sada djecu ubijati?"

616
00:37:29,000 --> 00:37:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže:

617
00:37:30,000 --> 00:37:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] "A mlada nedjelja!"

618
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prva nedjelja.

619
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] A oni su...

620
00:37:35,000 --> 00:37:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bili pravo, prazno vjeri.

621
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prazno vjeri su bili.

622
00:37:38,000 --> 00:37:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mlada nedjelja kućete, kaže:

623
00:37:40,000 --> 00:37:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Djecu i žene ubijati."

624
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] I vratili su se.

625
00:37:43,000 --> 00:37:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga,

626
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] 8.17.

627
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio mi išli drugi dan ili treći dan.

628
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Majka Božja, moja mama postila.

629
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čak i tu nedjelju je postila.

630
00:37:54,000 --> 00:37:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Danas Majka Božja spasi."

631
00:37:56,000 --> 00:37:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] I stvarno, došli italijani

632
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] i spasili ih.

633
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] I spasili su.

634
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda...

635
00:38:03,000 --> 00:38:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Otac je vidio:

636
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Nemate spasa, tu nema..."

637
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je pozvao

638
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] svoga prijatelja,

639
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] pobratima,

640
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] rekao:

641
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Uzmi ti sve.

642
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dajem ti sve.

643
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ozmi.

644
00:38:16,000 --> 00:38:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nosi kući.

645
00:38:17,000 --> 00:38:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja idem.

646
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bježim sa ti s obitelji."

647
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda smo mi...

648
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Preda smo preselili se u središtu

649
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] ta gradića

650
00:38:27,000 --> 00:38:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] i onda smo...

651
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tarlijani su nam dali kamion

652
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] da smo prešli sa Knin.

653
00:38:33,000 --> 00:38:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad smo došli u Knin,

654
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] tamo mi smo imali rodvine

655
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] koje su imali i dućane.

656
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] i došli smo najprek od jedne rodvine,

657
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] tamo smo odsijeli jednu noć,

658
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali moj tata nije htio biti da bude na teret.

659
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja neću biti na teret nikomu sa svojom obiteljom.

660
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] I šta je?

661
00:38:55,000 --> 00:39:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Došli su u dodir sa Ninom Sarića,

662
00:39:00,000 --> 00:39:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji je bilo iz drugog sela,

663
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] i sa...

664
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da Duić...

665
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se zvao?

666
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dvije bio obitelji.

667
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su išli za Požegu.

668
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Rekli su:

669
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Dođi s nama za Požegu.

670
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ukrčajmo i tvoje stvari subito u vagone,

671
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] pa dođi s nama."

672
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] I moj otac je prihvatio,

673
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] bili su prijatelji,

674
00:39:19,000 --> 00:39:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] izpoznavali su se,

675
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] i od nas ukrcao sve što smo donijeli.

676
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ukrcali su, dakle,

677
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] na te kamione,

678
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] te...

679
00:39:27,000 --> 00:39:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se kaže?

680
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] U vagone.

681
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] U vagone.

682
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] I oni su otišli.

683
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mi smo trebali sljedeći dan ići,

684
00:39:36,000 --> 00:39:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali trebali smo prije izvaditi dokumente,

685
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer nismo mogli putovati iz grada.

686
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Trebali smo imati dokumente.

687
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad zastao snijeg,

688
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] treći dan, snijeg u lici,

689
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne može vlakni nikuda.

690
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko ste ostali onda u...

691
00:39:53,000 --> 00:39:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda smo ostali do trećeg mjeseca.

692
00:39:56,000 --> 00:40:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zamisli, od decembra, tri mjesece.

693
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tri mjesece.

694
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bezišta.

695
00:40:03,000 --> 00:40:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bijeda.

696
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] U Krinu je bio glad.

697
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Siromaštvo.

698
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, ovi naši, dakle, rodbina,

699
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji put je dali nešto.

700
00:40:14,000 --> 00:40:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj otac nije htio.

701
00:40:16,000 --> 00:40:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nismo imali novaca.

702
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nismo mi bili jedni.

703
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako smo izgubili...

704
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Novaca smo imali.

705
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, onda...

706
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] A nije se moglo kupiti?

707
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nema kruha, ne možeš kupiti.

708
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedino što smo mogli kupiti,

709
00:40:30,000 --> 00:40:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] suhi šliva i bombona.

710
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Brat i Marko.

711
00:40:35,000 --> 00:40:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Najviše smo sjeli šluhe šlive.

712
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene bih za doručak kupili pet bombona.

713
00:40:41,000 --> 00:40:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Neki svileni bomboni su bili.

714
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pet bombona i doručak.

715
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Po sreći.

716
00:40:47,000 --> 00:40:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja uvijek hodala po gradu.

717
00:40:51,000 --> 00:40:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znam ti živna.

718
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta ono šta nadal tam.

719
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad baš ja se vraćam i jedan ofic...

720
00:40:59,000 --> 00:41:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] blizu nas je bila nastamba.

721
00:41:01,000 --> 00:41:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vojnička nastamba.

722
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo bili u nastambi za železniščare.

723
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer moj rođak, tato je bratić, bio železniščar.

724
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] I oni nas uveo.

725
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, bili su prazni.

726
00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže: "Dođite makar da imate krvo nad glavom".

727
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo mi to bili.

728
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo blizu kolodvora.

729
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] I bila je ta kasarna.

730
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vojnička.

731
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naša kasarna.

732
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad jedan oficer sa prozora mašem.

733
00:41:33,000 --> 00:41:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja si jednom.

734
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znati željno šta će.

735
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] I siđe on stepenica.

736
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] I pita me: "Pa šta ti tražeš?"

737
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem: "Mamu, kažem ja...

738
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Otkuda sam?"

739
00:41:45,000 --> 00:41:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem: "Iz Bosarskog grahova.

740
00:41:47,000 --> 00:41:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tu smo izbjegli.

741
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nemamo ništa."

742
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on men dane kruhi i po.

743
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže mi: "Sutra i svaki dan dođi.

744
00:41:56,000 --> 00:42:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Donesti zdjelicu i stavi se u red s vojnicima.

745
00:42:01,000 --> 00:42:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dati dadnom hranu."

746
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja dođim kuću.

747
00:42:06,000 --> 00:42:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj otac stric.

748
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] On donesem kruh i po.

749
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, tako.

750
00:42:13,000 --> 00:42:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, to ti je radost.

751
00:42:15,000 --> 00:42:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kažem: "Ja ću i sada uznem jednu zdjelicu.

752
00:42:18,000 --> 00:42:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam kuću takva je bila.

753
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad idem ja i stavim se u red s vojnicima.

754
00:42:23,000 --> 00:42:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nazad vojnicima.

755
00:42:25,000 --> 00:42:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je ono, znaš, pikec malo.

756
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Devet godina.

757
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] I oni mene, dakle, zima bila.

758
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imala sam kapucić, sve, dakle.

759
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] I mene vojnici smiju se sa mnom, znaš.

760
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tata, curica, da snimam.

761
00:42:40,000 --> 00:42:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kad oni svi dobili su svoju porciju,

762
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda ja dođem na kazan

763
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] i onda meni dam punitvo.

764
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj šar.

765
00:42:49,000 --> 00:42:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nosim to u kući.

766
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem: "Hvala Bogu, tato."

767
00:42:52,000 --> 00:42:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, radio se obitelj.

768
00:42:54,000 --> 00:42:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Za obitelj.

769
00:42:55,000 --> 00:42:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, imaju nešto za povest.

770
00:42:57,000 --> 00:42:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tako je to trajalo.

771
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dok nismo, kad se oslobodila recimo ta pruga,

772
00:43:03,000 --> 00:43:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda smo opet odšli za požegu.

773
00:43:07,000 --> 00:43:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo smo došli.

774
00:43:08,000 --> 00:43:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovi naši prijatelji, oni su nam našli stan

775
00:43:13,000 --> 00:43:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] na jednoj kući.

776
00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svak je imao jednu sobu za prvu silu.

777
00:43:18,000 --> 00:43:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo onda bili tamo.

778
00:43:20,000 --> 00:43:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda smo tamo se dosta dobro snašli.

779
00:43:23,000 --> 00:43:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj otac je odnos pošao raditi na Glatesu

780
00:43:27,000 --> 00:43:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] kao obrtnik.

781
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer on je poznavao bilo kovački.

782
00:43:37,000 --> 00:43:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo tišljarski zanat.

783
00:43:39,000 --> 00:43:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je umogao raditi.

784
00:43:41,000 --> 00:43:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Stric je u Klopji, isto u posao.

785
00:43:44,000 --> 00:43:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Malo je pomagao častnim sestrama.

786
00:43:46,000 --> 00:43:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Malo je jednoj našoj sljakinji.

787
00:43:48,000 --> 00:43:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo na gornji emovci.

788
00:43:51,000 --> 00:43:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Blizu su bili.

789
00:43:53,000 --> 00:43:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa tako da smo se mi snašli.

790
00:43:55,000 --> 00:43:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da smo odmora radili.

791
00:43:57,000 --> 00:43:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] I mjerovan nije ništa farevo.

792
00:43:59,000 --> 00:44:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer smo...

793
00:44:00,000 --> 00:44:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Super.

794
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prirago što odemo baš na požegu koji bi isto htio da malo prođemo zajedno,

795
00:44:05,000 --> 00:44:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] htio bi se vratiti na nekoliko događaja koji su bili u Grahovu,

796
00:44:09,000 --> 00:44:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji su obilježili to mjesto.

797
00:44:13,000 --> 00:44:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo od njih je sam don Juraj Gospodnečić koji je bio vaš župak.

798
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Juraj Gospodnečić je bio mladi svečenik.

799
00:44:22,000 --> 00:44:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je jako zauzeto.

800
00:44:27,000 --> 00:44:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] s nama djecom se puno angažirao.

801
00:44:31,000 --> 00:44:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] E recimo i možda je on tu...

802
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njegova možda pogreška je moj bila.

803
00:44:39,000 --> 00:44:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] To su mu ovih pravoslavni uključili.

804
00:44:45,000 --> 00:44:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] zamjerili možda.

805
00:44:47,000 --> 00:44:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je bio Sveti Ivan 24. lipnja,

806
00:44:51,000 --> 00:44:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda je on nama djecu pozvao nas.

807
00:44:54,000 --> 00:44:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da idemo u svaku kuću da donesemo pepela.

808
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] A on je imao kante petroleja.

809
00:45:04,000 --> 00:45:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad trebali smo napraviti od pepela te kugle.

810
00:45:10,000 --> 00:45:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda smo stavili iznad našeg sela,

811
00:45:13,000 --> 00:45:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] to je bjelo brežuljak iznad našeg sela.

812
00:45:16,000 --> 00:45:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tako ćemo svetnjak napraviti.

813
00:45:19,000 --> 00:45:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili smo palili svetnjake.

814
00:45:21,000 --> 00:45:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da ne pali svak za sebe svetnjak,

815
00:45:23,000 --> 00:45:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] napravit ćemo to da svi zajedno to odakle zapalimo.

816
00:45:29,000 --> 00:45:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] A neki dečki, znaš kao dečki,

817
00:45:32,000 --> 00:45:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] oni napravi i za toga naprave veliki žap.

818
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

819
00:45:37,000 --> 00:45:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Žap, naravno, to su gustaše.

820
00:45:41,000 --> 00:45:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Srbi vidjeli.

821
00:45:42,000 --> 00:45:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ili li vidjeli?

822
00:45:43,000 --> 00:45:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] E, pa ja.

823
00:45:44,000 --> 00:45:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad smo mi sve to zapali,

824
00:45:45,000 --> 00:45:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] svi drugi sela su vidili,

825
00:45:47,000 --> 00:45:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] a šta gore, obljajčani gore.

826
00:45:50,000 --> 00:45:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je tako bilo jasno, znaš šta.

827
00:45:53,000 --> 00:45:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, i to je, mi smo možda tu po...

828
00:45:56,000 --> 00:46:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ovi, znaš kako, dečki bili previše entuzijasti.

829
00:46:01,000 --> 00:46:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] I taj entuzijazam je nas...

830
00:46:04,000 --> 00:46:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koštao.

831
00:46:05,000 --> 00:46:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koštao.

832
00:46:06,000 --> 00:46:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koštao.

833
00:46:07,000 --> 00:46:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] i tekako.

834
00:46:08,000 --> 00:46:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da je to njega...

835
00:46:10,000 --> 00:46:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle...

836
00:46:11,000 --> 00:46:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer je on nas vodije...

837
00:46:13,000 --> 00:46:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Župnik je to napravio.

838
00:46:15,000 --> 00:46:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] A on nije bio kriv.

839
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] To su dečki kad bili.

840
00:46:18,000 --> 00:46:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] A šta ćeši kad je tako se dogodilo?

841
00:46:21,000 --> 00:46:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njega su...

842
00:46:22,000 --> 00:46:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je kad je napad bio...

843
00:46:24,000 --> 00:46:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je od...

844
00:46:26,000 --> 00:46:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] hosti je sve...

845
00:46:28,000 --> 00:46:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle...

846
00:46:29,000 --> 00:46:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle...

847
00:46:30,000 --> 00:46:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Konsumirao.

848
00:46:31,000 --> 00:46:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda...

849
00:46:32,000 --> 00:46:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve vada stavio u kuću.

850
00:46:36,000 --> 00:46:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali poslije smo mi to ipak spasili te posude.

851
00:46:39,000 --> 00:46:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svedebu.

852
00:46:40,000 --> 00:46:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koje su služile za Euharistiju.

853
00:46:44,000 --> 00:46:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on se je pobjegao među Sariće.

854
00:46:47,000 --> 00:46:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se sjećam...

855
00:46:48,000 --> 00:46:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je večer.

856
00:46:49,000 --> 00:46:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Suton je bio.

857
00:46:51,000 --> 00:46:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Maja sestra je zatvorila ovce.

858
00:46:53,000 --> 00:46:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ta štalu od ovaca.

859
00:46:55,000 --> 00:46:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] i kaže:

860
00:46:56,000 --> 00:46:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Mama, mama župnika su našli.

861
00:46:59,000 --> 00:47:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Župnika vode."

862
00:47:01,000 --> 00:47:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer naša štala je bila uz cestu.

863
00:47:05,000 --> 00:47:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ona je bila četnici pred njim i zajimim s puškama.

864
00:47:09,000 --> 00:47:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] A on zove Naco, moli za me.

865
00:47:13,000 --> 00:47:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je pozvao Naco.

866
00:47:15,000 --> 00:47:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ona je svaku strahu od nej shvatila šta je.

867
00:47:19,000 --> 00:47:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Došla.

868
00:47:20,000 --> 00:47:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je tata čuo, kaže:

869
00:47:22,000 --> 00:47:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Gotovo je.

870
00:47:23,000 --> 00:47:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Neće mu biti spasa."

871
00:47:25,000 --> 00:47:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Neće mu biti spasa.

872
00:47:26,000 --> 00:47:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nažalost, katolik je bez svećenik.

873
00:47:31,000 --> 00:47:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gotovo je.

874
00:47:33,000 --> 00:47:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tamo su ga mučili svaki dan.

875
00:47:37,000 --> 00:47:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] i na koncu je došao jedan praoslavac, prijatelj moga tate.

876
00:47:43,000 --> 00:47:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] i rekao da su ga pekli živa.

877
00:47:46,000 --> 00:47:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njega i Tomislava.

878
00:47:49,000 --> 00:47:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Najpred su ih dobro izmlatili.

879
00:47:51,000 --> 00:47:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro ih izmučili.

880
00:47:53,000 --> 00:47:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su ih žive pekli.

881
00:47:55,000 --> 00:47:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da čak su se rugali:

882
00:47:58,000 --> 00:48:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Pope, hoćeš mesa."

883
00:48:01,000 --> 00:48:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je grozato.

884
00:48:03,000 --> 00:48:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako su se izživljavali nad tim ljudima.

885
00:48:08,000 --> 00:48:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zamislite kako je to bilo grozno.

886
00:48:10,000 --> 00:48:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je tako meni se...

887
00:48:12,000 --> 00:48:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] A to je tata nama rekao:

888
00:48:14,000 --> 00:48:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ko ostane živ, to mora prenijeti."

889
00:48:18,000 --> 00:48:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zato kažem, ja se osjećam dužna da rečem istinu.

890
00:48:24,000 --> 00:48:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što se dogodilo?

891
00:48:25,000 --> 00:48:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Što su činili ti ljudi?

892
00:48:27,000 --> 00:48:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta im je župnik napravio?

893
00:48:29,000 --> 00:48:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] S njima je bilo u dobrim odnosima.

894
00:48:31,000 --> 00:48:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sa našim praoslavcima.

895
00:48:33,000 --> 00:48:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je bilo u dobrim odnosima.

896
00:48:35,000 --> 00:48:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad nije bilo prepiran između njega

897
00:48:37,000 --> 00:48:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] ili recimo srstvog praoslavnog papa.

898
00:48:40,000 --> 00:48:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili su ljudi...

899
00:48:42,000 --> 00:48:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ovi koji su sigurno došli iz drugih krajeva.

900
00:48:46,000 --> 00:48:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] To su li tako grozni, tako očajno.

901
00:48:51,000 --> 00:48:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je neopisivo.

902
00:48:55,000 --> 00:48:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njega i Tomislava oba.

903
00:48:58,000 --> 00:49:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] A nakon prije to...

904
00:49:00,000 --> 00:49:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Iza toga jednog dana dovedeše cijelu obitelj u našu kuću.

905
00:49:07,000 --> 00:49:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kažu: "Mami, ovi moraju isti kod vas tati."

906
00:49:12,000 --> 00:49:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Mama, dobro, primi ljude,

907
00:49:15,000 --> 00:49:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] dadi im jest, nahrani ih."

908
00:49:18,000 --> 00:49:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njih je bilo devetero.

909
00:49:21,000 --> 00:49:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, mama i osmero djece.

910
00:49:23,000 --> 00:49:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam uvijek mislela da je devetero djece.

911
00:49:25,000 --> 00:49:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je osmero djece i mama.

912
00:49:27,000 --> 00:49:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dijet, curice, bliznice.

913
00:49:29,000 --> 00:49:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šest mjeseci.

914
00:49:31,000 --> 00:49:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] A onda, znaš, ja s onim curicama odmah u igru...

915
00:49:35,000 --> 00:49:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

916
00:49:36,000 --> 00:49:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zaborališ se?

917
00:49:37,000 --> 00:49:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Djeca i svat, oni su kod nas prespavali jednu noć.

918
00:49:43,000 --> 00:49:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Drugi dan dođo še isti.

919
00:49:47,000 --> 00:49:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne.

920
00:49:48,000 --> 00:49:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni trebaju ići...

921
00:49:50,000 --> 00:49:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kod moje strine smo izvali.

922
00:49:55,000 --> 00:49:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Strine, ona je imala sina i čerku.

923
00:49:58,000 --> 00:50:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sin je Nikica bio, ih čerka.

924
00:50:01,000 --> 00:50:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Stana je bila smo izvali Čana.

925
00:50:04,000 --> 00:50:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo moraju ići.

926
00:50:07,000 --> 00:50:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Strina je primila ljude.

927
00:50:10,000 --> 00:50:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naše katolike.

928
00:50:12,000 --> 00:50:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mamo sad osmero djece.

929
00:50:15,000 --> 00:50:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] I da lejne u jednu sobu.

930
00:50:17,000 --> 00:50:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ima lejesto veliku sobu.

931
00:50:19,000 --> 00:50:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da lejne, tako da su oni bili.

932
00:50:21,000 --> 00:50:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali oni su poslije došli.

933
00:50:24,000 --> 00:50:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da oni moraju preko dana biti u župnom stanu.

934
00:50:29,000 --> 00:50:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] A preko noći spavati.

935
00:50:32,000 --> 00:50:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

936
00:50:33,000 --> 00:50:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda, naravno, mama i strina njima su dali za hranu.

937
00:50:38,000 --> 00:50:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da si mogu nešto skuhati.

938
00:50:40,000 --> 00:50:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tako da djecu prehrane.

939
00:50:42,000 --> 00:50:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sigurno pomažeš ljudima.

940
00:50:46,000 --> 00:50:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala Bogu imaš dosta.

941
00:50:47,000 --> 00:50:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imaš brašna.

942
00:50:48,000 --> 00:50:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imaš masti.

943
00:50:50,000 --> 00:50:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] U kući je bilo svega.

944
00:50:52,000 --> 00:50:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala Bogu.

945
00:50:53,000 --> 00:50:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da su oni tamo si hranili.

946
00:50:56,000 --> 00:50:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je trajalo nekoliko dana.

947
00:50:58,000 --> 00:51:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad ja ne znam točno koliko.

948
00:51:00,000 --> 00:51:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nese sam se točno.

949
00:51:03,000 --> 00:51:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svakako oni su tamo spavali.

950
00:51:05,000 --> 00:51:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad su jednu noć.

951
00:51:07,000 --> 00:51:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znam da Marija imala 20 godina.

952
00:51:11,000 --> 00:51:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Najstarija je bila.

953
00:51:13,000 --> 00:51:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je bio mladić.

954
00:51:14,000 --> 00:51:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možda 16 godina.

955
00:51:16,000 --> 00:51:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda druge su curice bile s jedna.

956
00:51:19,000 --> 00:51:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da su.

957
00:51:20,000 --> 00:51:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se igrala s njima.

958
00:51:22,000 --> 00:51:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Osobito se sjećala sam se s jednom curicom.

959
00:51:25,000 --> 00:51:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Lavorka se zvala.

960
00:51:27,000 --> 00:51:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Igrali smo se.

961
00:51:28,000 --> 00:51:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kao djeca.

962
00:51:29,000 --> 00:51:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle bilo nam je.

963
00:51:32,000 --> 00:51:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Djeca su nedižna.

964
00:51:35,000 --> 00:51:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ne znam šta ih sve čeka.

965
00:51:38,000 --> 00:51:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jednu noć kad su djeca već skoro pospala.

966
00:51:42,000 --> 00:51:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kod moje strine.

967
00:51:44,000 --> 00:51:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dođu dvojica.

968
00:51:46,000 --> 00:51:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dište se.

969
00:51:48,000 --> 00:51:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idite spavat u župnu.

970
00:51:50,000 --> 00:51:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle u kuću sveštenika.

971
00:51:53,000 --> 00:51:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moja mama.

972
00:51:56,000 --> 00:51:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle ona je rekla.

973
00:51:58,000 --> 00:51:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nemoj ništa.

974
00:51:59,000 --> 00:52:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naći ćemo sve.

975
00:52:01,000 --> 00:52:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] I oni su tači.

976
00:52:04,000 --> 00:52:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Djeca već pospano.

977
00:52:08,000 --> 00:52:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Digne djecu.

978
00:52:10,000 --> 00:52:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Diže su ih.

979
00:52:11,000 --> 00:52:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda maja strina kaže.

980
00:52:13,000 --> 00:52:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čerke i sinu.

981
00:52:14,000 --> 00:52:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pomozite im nositi stvari.

982
00:52:16,000 --> 00:52:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da makali pokrivače.

983
00:52:18,000 --> 00:52:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da prostoru da mogu zaspati.

984
00:52:22,000 --> 00:52:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer u župnika nema ništa.

985
00:52:24,000 --> 00:52:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve je to pokradeno.

986
00:52:26,000 --> 00:52:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve je odnešeno.

987
00:52:27,000 --> 00:52:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad.

988
00:52:28,000 --> 00:52:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sprate ih u kuhinu.

989
00:52:30,000 --> 00:52:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] A za vrata župna crkve.

990
00:52:35,000 --> 00:52:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bila su u staklu.

991
00:52:37,000 --> 00:52:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan dio bio u staklu.

992
00:52:38,000 --> 00:52:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je bio hodnik.

993
00:52:40,000 --> 00:52:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na jednoj strani je bila jedna soba.

994
00:52:43,000 --> 00:52:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su bile stepenice gore za spavanje.

995
00:52:46,000 --> 00:52:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] A dolje je bila kuhinja.

996
00:52:48,000 --> 00:52:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle peć.

997
00:52:50,000 --> 00:52:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle za drvarnicu.

998
00:52:52,000 --> 00:52:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bila je kao jedna u...

999
00:52:54,000 --> 00:52:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ulačak.

1000
00:52:55,000 --> 00:52:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ulačak.

1001
00:52:56,000 --> 00:53:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] jedan dio tako malo u zidu.

1002
00:53:00,000 --> 00:53:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] I njih strpaju sve.

1003
00:53:02,000 --> 00:53:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle u kuhinju.

1004
00:53:04,000 --> 00:53:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] U kuhinji je bio sto veliki stol.

1005
00:53:06,000 --> 00:53:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje su vada i jeli.

1006
00:53:07,000 --> 00:53:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad...

1007
00:53:09,000 --> 00:53:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Najprije pozovu moju tu rodicu.

1008
00:53:15,000 --> 00:53:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čanu.

1009
00:53:16,000 --> 00:53:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nju izvedu najprije.

1010
00:53:18,000 --> 00:53:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sa ovim...

1011
00:53:21,000 --> 00:53:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bodežom.

1012
00:53:23,000 --> 00:53:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] U nogu.

1013
00:53:24,000 --> 00:53:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] I baš u propanu.

1014
00:53:26,000 --> 00:53:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle.

1015
00:53:27,000 --> 00:53:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je odmah razumila šta je.

1016
00:53:29,000 --> 00:53:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imala je oko 13 godina.

1017
00:53:31,000 --> 00:53:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam njihova.

1018
00:53:33,000 --> 00:53:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odmah razumila šta o čemu se radi.

1019
00:53:36,000 --> 00:53:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] I oni su je stavili iza leđa.

1020
00:53:39,000 --> 00:53:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ne vidi...

1021
00:53:41,000 --> 00:53:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle da...

1022
00:53:42,000 --> 00:53:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne...

1023
00:53:43,000 --> 00:53:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da vidi šta oni rade.

1024
00:53:45,000 --> 00:53:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ona je onda su mamu izveli.

1025
00:53:48,000 --> 00:53:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže da su je sa sabljom preko leđa.

1026
00:53:52,000 --> 00:53:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je pala.

1027
00:53:53,000 --> 00:53:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su posle opet...

1028
00:53:54,000 --> 00:53:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili su odglavi.

1029
00:53:56,000 --> 00:53:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili šta je.

1030
00:53:57,000 --> 00:53:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su...

1031
00:53:58,000 --> 00:53:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dečka.

1032
00:53:59,000 --> 00:54:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda curi su jednu po jednu šestero.

1033
00:54:02,000 --> 00:54:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] ih je raz...

1034
00:54:04,000 --> 00:54:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pred njom su je ubili šestero.

1035
00:54:06,000 --> 00:54:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda kad su rekli:

1036
00:54:08,000 --> 00:54:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sada idi kući.

1037
00:54:09,000 --> 00:54:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] I nikom ne smiješ ništa reći.

1038
00:54:11,000 --> 00:54:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ona je jedna došla kući.

1039
00:54:13,000 --> 00:54:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ona se počela hladiti.

1040
00:54:15,000 --> 00:54:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je došla kući.

1041
00:54:18,000 --> 00:54:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pala je na pragu.

1042
00:54:19,000 --> 00:54:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mama.

1043
00:54:20,000 --> 00:54:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mama.

1044
00:54:21,000 --> 00:54:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je bila sva u krvi već.

1045
00:54:23,000 --> 00:54:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je razumjela šta je.

1046
00:54:27,000 --> 00:54:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Očajna.

1047
00:54:30,000 --> 00:54:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] A imala je samo tu kćerku i tog sina.

1048
00:54:33,000 --> 00:54:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su imali nakanu i ljubitih sina ili kćerku.

1049
00:54:37,000 --> 00:54:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] A pošto je sin njezin bio isto jako dobar kao moj brat Ivica.

1050
00:54:42,000 --> 00:54:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] To su bili dečki kao anđeli.

1051
00:54:45,000 --> 00:54:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dobre naravi.

1052
00:54:48,000 --> 00:54:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad nikom nisu nešto zlo rekli.

1053
00:54:51,000 --> 00:54:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto opakvu riječu ružnu.

1054
00:54:53,000 --> 00:54:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad ni Nikica ni moj brat Ivica.

1055
00:54:56,000 --> 00:54:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bili su...

1056
00:54:57,000 --> 00:54:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znam.

1057
00:54:58,000 --> 00:55:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam ih rakao da su bili anđeli.

1058
00:55:00,000 --> 00:55:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda vidili su ipak.

1059
00:55:02,000 --> 00:55:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] On ništa nije skrivio.

1060
00:55:04,000 --> 00:55:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1061
00:55:05,000 --> 00:55:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda smo u kćerku.

1062
00:55:06,000 --> 00:55:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedno mora nestati.

1063
00:55:09,000 --> 00:55:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da su...

1064
00:55:10,000 --> 00:55:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] No, ran li ona živjela sedam dana.

1065
00:55:13,000 --> 00:55:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odvijeli se u bolnicu ali gdje se bila već šepsi.

1066
00:55:17,000 --> 00:55:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bila veća infekcija.

1067
00:55:19,000 --> 00:55:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gotovo.

1068
00:55:20,000 --> 00:55:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ko zna kakve koljačke te koje imali su sredstva.

1069
00:55:24,000 --> 00:55:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da su...

1070
00:55:25,000 --> 00:55:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je ona umrla u roku šest dana.

1071
00:55:28,000 --> 00:55:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ove su onda...

1072
00:55:30,000 --> 00:55:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ostale su samo dvije bliznice i Marija najstarija.

1073
00:55:34,000 --> 00:55:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] A oni su vikali: "Marija, mi tebe nećemo."

1074
00:55:37,000 --> 00:55:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ta nećemo.

1075
00:55:38,000 --> 00:55:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna Marija.

1076
00:55:39,000 --> 00:55:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona se onda uvukla u tu rupu gdje su bila drva i drva presabodala.

1077
00:55:45,000 --> 00:55:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali oni su njoj izvukli na glavu i ocijekli.

1078
00:55:50,000 --> 00:55:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] A djecu su ovim malim bliznicama...

1079
00:55:53,000 --> 00:56:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na jednu su napravili šest bodeža na trbuhu, a drugo je na leđima.

1080
00:56:01,000 --> 00:56:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad zamislite, kaže...

1081
00:56:04,000 --> 00:56:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa jasno se pitala: "Pa šta su ti ljudi strevili?"

1082
00:56:09,000 --> 00:56:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njihov je otac bio lugar.

1083
00:56:14,000 --> 00:56:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad ja ne znam u jednom drugom selu, ja ne znam ko je to selo.

1084
00:56:19,000 --> 00:56:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam sva ta sela koje su bila.

1085
00:56:22,000 --> 00:56:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, lugar je bio i valjda Nehotice.

1086
00:56:26,000 --> 00:56:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan je valjda pravoslavac.

1087
00:56:28,000 --> 00:56:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, odrezao jedno stablo ili šta je bilo.

1088
00:56:34,000 --> 00:56:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on je valjda Nehotice njega ubio.

1089
00:56:37,000 --> 00:56:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to je bila osveta.

1090
00:56:40,000 --> 00:56:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njega su uhvatili.

1091
00:56:44,000 --> 00:56:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njega su toliko izmučili.

1092
00:56:48,000 --> 00:56:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mukčenja bacili su ga u jednu jamu.

1093
00:56:51,000 --> 00:56:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Podnosili tih jame bez danka.

1094
00:56:54,000 --> 00:56:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je kažu: "12 dana je ukao u jami."

1095
00:56:57,000 --> 00:57:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon toga su i njegovu obitelj.

1096
00:57:00,000 --> 00:57:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga njegovu cijelu obitelj uništili.

1097
00:57:03,000 --> 00:57:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imali su još jednog sina, on je bio ustašan.

1098
00:57:07,000 --> 00:57:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad ne znam kako je on završio.

1099
00:57:09,000 --> 00:57:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svakako...

1100
00:57:11,000 --> 00:57:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam ja došla u Grahovo,

1101
00:57:15,000 --> 00:57:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda rekli su oni da...

1102
00:57:18,000 --> 00:57:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam ja opisala to sve,

1103
00:57:20,000 --> 00:57:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda su rodina je deka došla.

1104
00:57:23,000 --> 00:57:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su htjeli mene pitati.

1105
00:57:25,000 --> 00:57:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali meni je išlo na plać.

1106
00:57:27,000 --> 00:57:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ja sam njih sve vidjela mrtve.

1107
00:57:32,000 --> 00:57:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam ja bila te curice mrtve...

1108
00:57:34,000 --> 00:57:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to je...

1109
00:57:35,000 --> 00:57:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je meni tako se...

1110
00:57:37,000 --> 00:57:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle...

1111
00:57:39,000 --> 00:57:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Upamtim li je toliko ostalo u pameti,

1112
00:57:42,000 --> 00:57:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] da ja nisam mogla zamisliti

1113
00:57:45,000 --> 00:57:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] da ti ljudi mogu nešto napraviti.

1114
00:57:48,000 --> 00:57:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da...

1115
00:57:50,000 --> 00:57:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda i treh dana bili su.

1116
00:57:52,000 --> 00:57:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Niko nije smio reći ništa.

1117
00:57:54,000 --> 00:57:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ipak moj otac...

1118
00:57:58,000 --> 00:57:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odeo.

1119
00:57:59,000 --> 00:58:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, ljudi...

1120
00:58:01,000 --> 00:58:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vi isto imate vjeru.

1121
00:58:03,000 --> 00:58:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vi vjerujete u Boga.

1122
00:58:06,000 --> 00:58:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog postoji.

1123
00:58:08,000 --> 00:58:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] I vas će kazniti.

1124
00:58:10,000 --> 00:58:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dozvolite, makar meni,

1125
00:58:12,000 --> 00:58:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] da ja te ljude pokopam.

1126
00:58:14,000 --> 00:58:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da ja te osobe, da tu djecu pokopam.

1127
00:58:18,000 --> 00:58:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda su mi dozvolili.

1128
00:58:21,000 --> 00:58:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda i još jedan naš rođak koji je ostao...

1129
00:58:25,000 --> 00:58:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, oni su stavili...

1130
00:58:26,000 --> 00:58:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, na kola.

1131
00:58:28,000 --> 00:58:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi je na kola su stavili.

1132
00:58:30,000 --> 00:58:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] I njihove te stvari...

1133
00:58:32,000 --> 00:58:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prosto su imali sa sobom.

1134
00:58:36,000 --> 00:58:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] I odveli...

1135
00:58:38,000 --> 00:58:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu mu dozvolili da odvede na grobneša.

1136
00:58:41,000 --> 00:58:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ma morali su...

1137
00:58:43,000 --> 00:58:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj otac i taj naš rođak...

1138
00:58:45,000 --> 00:58:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Morali su iskopati jamu na crkvenoj zemlji.

1139
00:58:50,000 --> 00:58:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, ja sam rekla u Kožegi.

1140
00:58:52,000 --> 00:58:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] U Grahovo.

1141
00:58:54,000 --> 00:58:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje je ta crkvena zemlja?

1142
00:58:55,000 --> 00:58:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znam točno mjesto.

1143
00:58:57,000 --> 00:58:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali znam da nije daleko.

1144
00:58:59,000 --> 00:59:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] I da je tamo...

1145
00:59:01,000 --> 00:59:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj otac iskopao tu veliku raku.

1146
00:59:03,000 --> 00:59:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Veliku jamu.

1147
00:59:06,000 --> 00:59:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Položje kaže da je stavio te...

1148
00:59:08,000 --> 00:59:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Te deke šta su imali najprije dolje.

1149
00:59:12,000 --> 00:59:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je stavio mamu i dakle čerku najstariju.

1150
00:59:16,000 --> 00:59:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže da je stavio te male crce u krilo jednoj mama, jednoj u maminoj krilu, a jednoj u sestrinoj.

1151
00:59:27,000 --> 00:59:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] druga je poredao i posle je pokrio po tim sinjim stavima i onda je zemlju natrpao.

1152
00:59:32,000 --> 00:59:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] A sljedeći dan je otišao i uzeo žicu i ogradio da ne bi životinje kopale to.

1153
00:59:40,000 --> 00:59:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su uzeli pik na moga oca.

1154
00:59:45,000 --> 00:59:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] da će i njega slistiti.

1155
00:59:46,000 --> 00:59:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo to zato što im je prigovorio?

1156
00:59:49,000 --> 00:59:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve prigovorio.

1157
00:59:51,000 --> 00:59:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, sad uzeli na njega pik.

1158
00:59:53,000 --> 00:59:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] I jedno pitanje samo.

1159
00:59:55,000 --> 01:00:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Htio bih se vratiti na opis koji ste dali u knjizi da je Marija dok su ju pokapali da je zasjela kao sunce.

1160
01:00:02,000 --> 01:00:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, eto. Tata je to rekao.

1161
01:00:04,000 --> 01:00:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je stavio Mariju, ona je zasjela kao sunce.

1162
01:00:08,000 --> 01:00:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] A dan prije, dan prije Marija je došla moje sestri.

1163
01:00:14,000 --> 01:00:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Sesto, molim te, malo sapuna i jednu ručnik."

1164
01:00:21,000 --> 01:00:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ona je išla na rijeku i okupala se.

1165
01:00:25,000 --> 01:00:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je moja sestra naca me rekla jer moja naca je imala oko 19 godina.

1166
01:00:31,000 --> 01:00:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ne, bile su više manji istih godina pa su se razumijele.

1167
01:00:35,000 --> 01:00:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, naca mu imala. Onda je dala ona sapun i ručnik da je otišla da se je oprala.

1168
01:00:43,000 --> 01:00:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bila je ona nevina djevojka i bila. Kaže, ona je zasjela kao sunce. To je nam je tata rekao.

1169
01:00:52,000 --> 01:01:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, a djeca su isto tako bila nevina od 14, 13, 9, 8 godina.

1170
01:01:01,000 --> 01:01:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo reći da je to u stvari pravo mučenještvo.

1171
01:01:03,000 --> 01:01:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pravo mučenještvo.

1172
01:01:05,000 --> 01:01:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to su bili svi nevini ljudi.

1173
01:01:08,000 --> 01:01:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Taj desko koji je imao 16 godina, 15, 16 godina, ma šta je učinio?

1174
01:01:14,000 --> 01:01:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1175
01:01:15,000 --> 01:01:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] A bio je, ja se sjećam, bio je dobar, kao kruh dečko.

1176
01:01:18,000 --> 01:01:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, evo, a to je groza. To je bila velika osveta.

1177
01:01:24,000 --> 01:01:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, kažem ti, to je tako strahovito.

1178
01:01:29,000 --> 01:01:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su svaku dečer, došao je opet jedan prijatelj mome otcu, pravoslavac.

1179
01:01:36,000 --> 01:01:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem ti, jer njega su ljudi jako volili u našem selu.

1180
01:01:38,000 --> 01:01:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, znaš šta, Mio, sada će ti pucati u kuću.

1181
01:01:43,000 --> 01:01:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne izlazi na balkon.

1182
01:01:46,000 --> 01:01:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne govori ništa.

1183
01:01:48,000 --> 01:01:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tvoja je kuća, neće se može probiti s jednim metkom.

1184
01:01:53,000 --> 01:01:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer kuća je bila od kamenja, dakle blokovi kamena.

1185
01:01:57,000 --> 01:02:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to ne može jedan metak probiti.

1186
01:02:00,000 --> 01:02:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, i tako da su onda svaku večer pucali su.

1187
01:02:06,000 --> 01:02:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] U kuću.

1188
01:02:07,000 --> 01:02:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali moj otac nije se pojajljiveo, nije šta govorio.

1189
01:02:10,000 --> 01:02:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste vi tada bili u kući dok su pucali?

1190
01:02:12,000 --> 01:02:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo bili uvijek u polju.

1191
01:02:15,000 --> 01:02:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo se uvijek sakrivali.

1192
01:02:17,000 --> 01:02:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1193
01:02:19,000 --> 01:02:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili u polju, ili...

1194
01:02:21,000 --> 01:02:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bože sačuvaj, ili popojali bi se na stablu.

1195
01:02:24,000 --> 01:02:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bože, šta čove kaže.

1196
01:02:26,000 --> 01:02:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, u Dagrahu ima dosta zmije.

1197
01:02:30,000 --> 01:02:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nas niko, nijedna zmija, ni u polju.

1198
01:02:34,000 --> 01:02:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] S koja zmije po noći oblicu kaže da izlazu zmije.

1199
01:02:36,000 --> 01:02:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, nas ni...

1200
01:02:38,000 --> 01:02:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi ništa nismo vidjeli.

1201
01:02:40,000 --> 01:02:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikakve zmije oko nas.

1202
01:02:42,000 --> 01:02:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bog vas je čuvao i na taj način.

1203
01:02:44,000 --> 01:02:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, kažem.

1204
01:02:46,000 --> 01:02:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem stvarno, jakaren dragi Bog je bio s nama.

1205
01:02:50,000 --> 01:02:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je nešuje.

1206
01:02:51,000 --> 01:02:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer bili smo nevini.

1207
01:02:52,000 --> 01:02:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bili smo nedužni.

1208
01:02:54,000 --> 01:02:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikom nismo učinili zla.

1209
01:02:56,000 --> 01:02:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] A jeste...

1210
01:02:58,000 --> 01:03:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tad ste imali devet godina.

1211
01:03:00,000 --> 01:03:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste svačali da se baš tako veliko zlo događa?

1212
01:03:03,000 --> 01:03:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste uspjeli naći nekakve radosti...

1213
01:03:06,000 --> 01:03:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znate šta?

1214
01:03:08,000 --> 01:03:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam...

1215
01:03:09,000 --> 01:03:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam bila svjetna da smo mi predmet mržnje.

1216
01:03:13,000 --> 01:03:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Srpske mržnje.

1217
01:03:16,000 --> 01:03:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je jasno bilo.

1218
01:03:17,000 --> 01:03:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kažem...

1219
01:03:19,000 --> 01:03:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja...

1220
01:03:21,000 --> 01:03:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je bilo glavno da sam ja uzio roditelje.

1221
01:03:25,000 --> 01:03:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] E oni su meni oslom bili.

1222
01:03:27,000 --> 01:03:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] I dragi Bog nas je čuvao.

1223
01:03:29,000 --> 01:03:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je to glavno bilo.

1224
01:03:31,000 --> 01:03:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je bio strah da ja ostanem sana.

1225
01:03:34,000 --> 01:03:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da nemam roditelja.

1226
01:03:36,000 --> 01:03:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uza se.

1227
01:03:38,000 --> 01:03:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Osobito mamu.

1228
01:03:39,000 --> 01:03:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1229
01:03:41,000 --> 01:03:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] U stvari domaće pravoslavnost.

1230
01:03:45,000 --> 01:03:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ništo vas je ispasilo na neki način.

1231
01:03:47,000 --> 01:03:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je.

1232
01:03:48,000 --> 01:03:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naši pravoslavci kažem...

1233
01:03:50,000 --> 01:03:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni nas nisu prezirali.

1234
01:03:52,000 --> 01:03:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kažem...

1235
01:03:54,000 --> 01:03:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sigurno ovaj koji je zaustavio taj...

1236
01:03:57,000 --> 01:03:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tu povorku...

1237
01:03:59,000 --> 01:04:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je vjerojatno bio iz našeg sela.

1238
01:04:02,000 --> 01:04:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on im je rekao pa ljudi šta...

1239
01:04:04,000 --> 01:04:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta radite sad?

1240
01:04:06,000 --> 01:04:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta hoćete?

1241
01:04:08,000 --> 01:04:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Danas je mlada nedjelja.

1242
01:04:09,000 --> 01:04:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže...

1243
01:04:12,000 --> 01:04:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] A žene i djeca šta su nam učinili?

1244
01:04:14,000 --> 01:04:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta su nam učinili?

1245
01:04:15,000 --> 01:04:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek s njim...

1246
01:04:17,000 --> 01:04:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su nama uvijek bili, mislim...

1247
01:04:18,000 --> 01:04:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prijazni, jedni s drugima.

1248
01:04:20,000 --> 01:04:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pozdravljali smo se.

1249
01:04:22,000 --> 01:04:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čak su se između sebe ženili.

1250
01:04:24,000 --> 01:04:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Recimo, i bili na vjenčanju.

1251
01:04:27,000 --> 01:04:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta ti ja znam?

1252
01:04:29,000 --> 01:04:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da...

1253
01:04:31,000 --> 01:04:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem ja s našim pravoslavcima...

1254
01:04:34,000 --> 01:04:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi nismo imali problema.

1255
01:04:37,000 --> 01:04:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] To su došli iz drugih kraja.

1256
01:04:39,000 --> 01:04:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Otkuda ja ne znam.

1257
01:04:40,000 --> 01:04:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da...

1258
01:04:42,000 --> 01:04:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] I bili su stvarno zlobni.

1259
01:04:44,000 --> 01:04:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] I bili su okrutni.

1260
01:04:46,000 --> 01:04:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako okrutne stvari su činili.

1261
01:04:49,000 --> 01:04:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Okrutne stvari.

1262
01:04:52,000 --> 01:04:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] mučerno što prava i do Nuraja i obitelji.

1263
01:04:55,000 --> 01:04:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je grozota, grozota što su cečniti radili.

1264
01:04:59,000 --> 01:05:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1265
01:05:01,000 --> 01:05:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta mislite koji je bio motiv za te zločine?

1266
01:05:03,000 --> 01:05:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Baš za to...

1267
01:05:05,000 --> 01:05:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] barbarstvo.

1268
01:05:06,000 --> 01:05:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako bi...

1269
01:05:09,000 --> 01:05:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta mislite? Koji je bio motiv osip toga što...

1270
01:05:12,000 --> 01:05:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znate šta?

1271
01:05:14,000 --> 01:05:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zato jer su izgubili državu.

1272
01:05:16,000 --> 01:05:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Propala je država.

1273
01:05:18,000 --> 01:05:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] One su uvijek htjeli imat' sve u rukama.

1274
01:05:21,000 --> 01:05:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zapravo je Jugoslavija stara.

1275
01:05:23,000 --> 01:05:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve je bilo u rukama pravoslavaca.

1276
01:05:26,000 --> 01:05:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] One su sve vodili.

1277
01:05:29,000 --> 01:05:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] U svogdje i u Bosni, Hercegovini, Hrvatskoj.

1278
01:05:33,000 --> 01:05:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje je bilo?

1279
01:05:34,000 --> 01:05:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] One su bili vođani.

1280
01:05:35,000 --> 01:05:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su spriječavali.

1281
01:05:36,000 --> 01:05:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čak kad je moj pokojni otac gradio kuću.

1282
01:05:40,000 --> 01:05:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda trebao je ciment.

1283
01:05:43,000 --> 01:05:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Morao je ići u Beograd molit'.

1284
01:05:46,000 --> 01:05:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ove mu nisu davali.

1285
01:05:49,000 --> 01:05:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je dobio da može ciment.

1286
01:05:52,000 --> 01:05:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, spriječavali su svaki napredak Hrvata.

1287
01:05:56,000 --> 01:05:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedino sjećam to.

1288
01:05:59,000 --> 01:06:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] To mi je rekla moja sestra Janja.

1289
01:06:02,000 --> 01:06:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njezin muž, Nikola Špiranović.

1290
01:06:07,000 --> 01:06:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je bio jako visok, fin čovjek.

1291
01:06:11,000 --> 01:06:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njega je otac od principa, Gavrila principa.

1292
01:06:16,000 --> 01:06:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njega je jako volio.

1293
01:06:19,000 --> 01:06:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on je rekao: "Slišaj, ti moraš biti u Kraljevoj gardi".

1294
01:06:25,000 --> 01:06:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on je njega preporučio.

1295
01:06:27,000 --> 01:06:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je Nina bio u Kraljevoj gardi u Beogradu.

1296
01:06:34,000 --> 01:06:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Toliko je bilo prijateljstvo.

1297
01:06:38,000 --> 01:06:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je toliko njega volio, a je ostao bez oca.

1298
01:06:41,000 --> 01:06:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] A majka mu se preudala.

1299
01:06:44,000 --> 01:06:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad je o toj, a bio je fin dečkost, jako fin.

1300
01:06:47,000 --> 01:06:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa recimo, a kod nas su bili ljudi jako visoki.

1301
01:06:51,000 --> 01:06:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] To su baš oni dinarci visoki.

1302
01:06:54,000 --> 01:06:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] I moj uvijek imao dva metra i deset.

1303
01:06:56,000 --> 01:06:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek ni Andreja.

1304
01:06:58,000 --> 01:07:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da...

1305
01:07:00,000 --> 01:07:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on je ti je bio u Kraljevoj gardi služio.

1306
01:07:04,000 --> 01:07:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači...

1307
01:07:06,000 --> 01:07:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nina.

1308
01:07:07,000 --> 01:07:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako bila, kažem, bila je tih dobrih...

1309
01:07:13,000 --> 01:07:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo je i dobrih strana i veze.

1310
01:07:16,000 --> 01:07:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, bila je ljudi dobrih.

1311
01:07:18,000 --> 01:07:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] A naravno, nađe se i znao čovjek.

1312
01:07:22,000 --> 01:07:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto? Ne znao čovjek.

1313
01:07:24,000 --> 01:07:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo se vratiti na požegu i na vaš život u požegi?

1314
01:07:29,000 --> 01:07:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj život u požegi.

1315
01:07:31,000 --> 01:07:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam došla...

1316
01:07:32,000 --> 01:07:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedina izbjeglica sam bila u školi.

1317
01:07:37,000 --> 01:07:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] U mom razredu.

1318
01:07:39,000 --> 01:07:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mala bosančica su me rekli.

1319
01:07:42,000 --> 01:07:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, hvala Bogu.

1320
01:07:44,000 --> 01:07:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad...

1321
01:07:46,000 --> 01:07:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tijela sam ići u treći razred.

1322
01:07:48,000 --> 01:07:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali pošto je bila na koncu školske godine.

1323
01:07:51,000 --> 01:07:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja sam znala bolje pisati i čitati čirilicu,

1324
01:07:55,000 --> 01:07:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] nego latinicu.

1325
01:07:57,000 --> 01:08:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer mi smo sve u čirilici pisali i čitali.

1326
01:08:01,000 --> 01:08:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Malo smo imali u drugom razredu,

1327
01:08:04,000 --> 01:08:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] malo možda mjesec ili ipo ako smo u latinice.

1328
01:08:08,000 --> 01:08:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam to mucala u latinici.

1329
01:08:12,000 --> 01:08:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su sestre, sestre su savjetavila mome ocu, bolje da ja idem u drugi razred, ova dva, tri mjeseca.

1330
01:08:21,000 --> 01:08:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zbog svega.

1331
01:08:22,000 --> 01:08:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zbog svega.

1332
01:08:23,000 --> 01:08:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je uplivalo na mene.

1333
01:08:24,000 --> 01:08:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda sam zaboravila mnoge stvari u tom strahu, u svemu.

1334
01:08:39,000 --> 01:08:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sam ja dva mjeseca i pol koja vratila se u drugi razred.

1335
01:08:44,000 --> 01:08:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako sam savršila ga to puno drugi.

1336
01:08:48,000 --> 01:08:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] i naučila dobru latinicu.

1337
01:08:50,000 --> 01:08:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sam poslije treći razred normalno počela i bila sam odličan džak među najboljima.

1338
01:08:56,000 --> 01:09:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ja sam bila, ja sam volila učit, volila sam čitat.

1339
01:09:00,000 --> 01:09:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sam ja brzo dostigla sve.

1340
01:09:04,000 --> 01:09:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako onda sestre su me zavolile.

1341
01:09:07,000 --> 01:09:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jednu stvar, ja nisam volila jest ujutro.

1342
01:09:14,000 --> 01:09:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] O, ujutro jest.

1343
01:09:16,000 --> 01:09:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] A puno sam spavila.

1344
01:09:18,000 --> 01:09:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam bila jako pospana ujep.

1345
01:09:20,000 --> 01:09:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Digli mene iz kreve, to je bio problem.

1346
01:09:23,000 --> 01:09:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad mama bih zala:

1347
01:09:25,000 --> 01:09:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde, sinko, diži se.

1348
01:09:26,000 --> 01:09:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zakasnićeš u školu.

1349
01:09:28,000 --> 01:09:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sinko, dižite.

1350
01:09:29,000 --> 01:09:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jed dođe, pa drugi put dođe, pa treće.

1351
01:09:31,000 --> 01:09:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Diži se, zakasnićeš.

1352
01:09:33,000 --> 01:09:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kada bi ja digla, onda bi brzo.

1353
01:09:36,000 --> 01:09:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Umerila se brzo obruča i bježim u školu.

1354
01:09:39,000 --> 01:09:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ne imala vremena za jest.

1355
01:09:41,000 --> 01:09:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne bih jela.

1356
01:09:44,000 --> 01:09:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da je danas, da je sutra.

1357
01:09:46,000 --> 01:09:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda moja sestra...

1358
01:09:48,000 --> 01:09:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda vam kaže:

1359
01:09:50,000 --> 01:09:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moja sestra, naci, idi ti častnim sestrama.

1360
01:09:53,000 --> 01:09:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Reci da ona nikada ne jede ujutro.

1361
01:09:56,000 --> 01:09:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad ona ide direktorica.

1362
01:09:59,000 --> 01:10:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] A direktorica bog dao bija stroga sestra Josipa.

1363
01:10:03,000 --> 01:10:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Malešna, ali stroga, da bog sačuje.

1364
01:10:07,000 --> 01:10:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona dođe Sarić u razred.

1365
01:10:09,000 --> 01:10:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jesi doručkovala?

1366
01:10:11,000 --> 01:10:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam.

1367
01:10:13,000 --> 01:10:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona mene tako blokirala, da ja nikad nisam mogla slagat.

1368
01:10:16,000 --> 01:10:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam mogla neći.

1369
01:10:18,000 --> 01:10:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jesam.

1370
01:10:20,000 --> 01:10:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam.

1371
01:10:21,000 --> 01:10:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] U kuhinu.

1372
01:10:22,000 --> 01:10:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek iskreno je bilo.

1373
01:10:23,000 --> 01:10:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo.

1374
01:10:26,000 --> 01:10:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je često bilo.

1375
01:10:28,000 --> 01:10:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Skoro svaki dan čim ja došla u školu, Sarić je sjela.

1376
01:10:34,000 --> 01:10:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam.

1377
01:10:35,000 --> 01:10:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koji puta?

1378
01:10:38,000 --> 01:10:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda bi ja šla u moram ići u kuhinu.

1379
01:10:40,000 --> 01:10:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad bila je jedna častna sestra koja bi mi dala polijente i mlijeka.

1380
01:10:46,000 --> 01:10:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja toga nisam molila.

1381
01:10:48,000 --> 01:10:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona bi rekla: žrtvice za misije.

1382
01:10:53,000 --> 01:10:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Što ja se žrtvice za misije?

1383
01:10:57,000 --> 01:10:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Puno ste se žrtvovali.

1384
01:10:59,000 --> 01:11:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uuu, Bože, sad čuje.

1385
01:11:02,000 --> 01:11:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] A kad je bila druga sestra, Blagojica se zvala, ona bi mi dala gibanice.

1386
01:11:07,000 --> 01:11:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde to ipak nešto.

1387
01:11:09,000 --> 01:11:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, gibanice ja pojela i bjeđem.

1388
01:11:12,000 --> 01:11:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] E onda, a moraš i na ručku ostati.

1389
01:11:15,000 --> 01:11:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] I poslije podne mi smo imali vježbe na stadionu.

1390
01:11:21,000 --> 01:11:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Djevojke iz gimnazije, one su nam imali vježbe.

1391
01:11:28,000 --> 01:11:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda dva, tri puta tjedno morali smo ostati.

1392
01:11:31,000 --> 01:11:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda osobito u mjesecu svibnju i listopadu bio je blagoslov poslije podne.

1393
01:11:39,000 --> 01:11:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da se mene nije isplaćalo ići dakle u kući.

1394
01:11:44,000 --> 01:11:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bi napravila zadaću i onda bi išla sestri u štalu.

1395
01:11:49,000 --> 01:11:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam volila, tamo su bili ozecevi, pa bile su pilići.

1396
01:11:55,000 --> 01:11:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja sam to volila.

1397
01:11:57,000 --> 01:11:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Životinice.

1398
01:11:58,000 --> 01:12:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Životinice.

1399
01:12:00,000 --> 01:12:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda bi mena dala da naklani piliće ili naklani recimo ove zeceve.

1400
01:12:08,000 --> 01:12:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja to volila.

1401
01:12:11,000 --> 01:12:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je mene jedan put darovala.

1402
01:12:13,000 --> 01:12:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jednog bijalog zeca i jednog crnog.

1403
01:12:17,000 --> 01:12:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo.

1404
01:12:20,000 --> 01:12:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja došla sa zecevima kuće.

1405
01:12:22,000 --> 01:12:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda moj otac napravio me gajbe.

1406
01:12:25,000 --> 01:12:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, to je bilo užitak.

1407
01:12:28,000 --> 01:12:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bila sestra Borgija se zvala.

1408
01:12:31,000 --> 01:12:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Sestri Borgija, mogu vam šta pomoći?"

1409
01:12:34,000 --> 01:12:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona mi rekla.

1410
01:12:36,000 --> 01:12:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Znaš te, ja ću bit častna sestra."

1411
01:12:38,000 --> 01:12:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam njoj rekla.

1412
01:12:40,000 --> 01:12:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ja ću bit častna sestra."

1413
01:12:41,000 --> 01:12:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] I baš da je ona to rekla drugima.

1414
01:12:43,000 --> 01:12:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je bila klica poziva od vas.

1415
01:12:46,000 --> 01:12:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ja sam volila.

1416
01:12:48,000 --> 01:12:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se sjećam jedna druga sestra.

1417
01:12:52,000 --> 01:12:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Starija je bila.

1418
01:12:54,000 --> 01:12:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda bi mene pozvala s prozora.

1419
01:12:58,000 --> 01:12:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sarić.

1420
01:12:59,000 --> 01:13:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bi došla gore.

1421
01:13:01,000 --> 01:13:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja dala bi mi jabuku.

1422
01:13:03,000 --> 01:13:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] A sestra koja je bila u kapeli, koja je imala kapelu na važu,

1423
01:13:08,000 --> 01:13:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] ona je imala ovaj...

1424
01:13:11,000 --> 01:13:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pozdala bi me više puta da je obrišem, dakle, neke aspedistre.

1425
01:13:18,000 --> 01:13:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] To su te, mislim, te listovi.

1426
01:13:22,000 --> 01:13:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] I da ja to prašeno obrišem.

1427
01:13:26,000 --> 01:13:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda bi na koncu bi mi dala hostije od komadića od hostije, jer ona je bila sakristanka.

1428
01:13:32,000 --> 01:13:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda bi mi dala hostije.

1429
01:13:34,000 --> 01:13:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda bi ja došla doli curicama dijela, dakle, to ostaje.

1430
01:13:38,000 --> 01:13:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] To bi bilo veselje.

1431
01:13:40,000 --> 01:13:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, da su mene sestre volile.

1432
01:13:43,000 --> 01:13:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam doživjela da one mene jako vole.

1433
01:13:47,000 --> 01:13:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Za vrijeme ferija ona bi meni dala puno glasnika.

1434
01:13:55,000 --> 01:14:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Glasnik svjetog Josipa, zlatih svjetog Ante, onda vrtić je bio za djecu, onda je bio anđel čuvar.

1435
01:14:02,000 --> 01:14:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona bi meni dala puno toga da ja čitam.

1436
01:14:06,000 --> 01:14:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam cijelo ljeto čitala.

1437
01:14:08,000 --> 01:14:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ja sam se načitala, a od prijateljica sam pozunila knjige.

1438
01:14:15,000 --> 01:14:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan put mi je jedna posudila Petricu Kerempuha.

1439
01:14:19,000 --> 01:14:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bio jedan dečko koji je izvađao svake smješnice i tako.

1440
01:14:23,000 --> 01:14:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, koje nisu baš za curice.

1441
01:14:27,000 --> 01:14:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad moj otac je vidio: "Ja se smijem, čitam to i smijem se, znaš?"

1442
01:14:32,000 --> 01:14:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, moj otac, šta ona čita da vidi Petrica Kerempuha?

1443
01:14:37,000 --> 01:14:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ko ti je to dao?"

1444
01:14:38,000 --> 01:14:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ja ću ti je baciti u vatru."

1445
01:14:40,000 --> 01:14:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ne, moj tata, molim te, ja ću to odmah vratiti."

1446
01:14:44,000 --> 01:14:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] A da, i morala sam sve odmah vratiti knjigu, ali ja sam pročitala.

1447
01:14:47,000 --> 01:14:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pročitala pa vratila.

1448
01:14:50,000 --> 01:14:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, ja sam puno čitala.

1449
01:14:53,000 --> 01:14:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je meni jedan svećaner rekao:

1450
01:14:55,000 --> 01:15:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Pa otkuda ti imaš tako lijepi riječnik u hrvatskom jeziku?"

1451
01:15:00,000 --> 01:15:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja sam čitala.

1452
01:15:02,000 --> 01:15:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda kažem, sve te pomoći što su bile za djevojnike, ranjene vojnike,

1453
01:15:08,000 --> 01:15:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] koje je moj stric meni kupovao pa dao, ja sam sve to čitala.

1454
01:15:12,000 --> 01:15:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bila je priča, bilo je sva razni događaje

1455
01:15:15,000 --> 01:15:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] i bila je ta lijepa pjesmica koju se ima naučila na pamet odmah.

1456
01:15:19,000 --> 01:15:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] A bila dugačka je bila, ali meni se sviđalo, ja sam to odmah naučila na pamet.

1457
01:15:25,000 --> 01:15:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja još danas poloviću znam na pamet.

1458
01:15:27,000 --> 01:15:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, a to je meni se to...

1459
01:15:30,000 --> 01:15:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja volim pjesmu inače, volim pjesmu.

1460
01:15:33,000 --> 01:15:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ti volim pjesmu.

1461
01:15:36,000 --> 01:15:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Razne stvari.

1462
01:15:41,000 --> 01:15:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Volila sam ples, pjesmu.

1463
01:15:43,000 --> 01:15:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda, recimo, priredbe.

1464
01:15:48,000 --> 01:15:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je meni bilo sve nekako prirođeno.

1465
01:15:50,000 --> 01:15:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je bilo umjetnički u vama.

1466
01:15:54,000 --> 01:15:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] I u Požegi ste koliko dugo živjeli?

1467
01:15:58,000 --> 01:16:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Od 42. od marta, trežne, do 44. do 6. decembra.

1468
01:16:08,000 --> 01:16:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, dvije godine i po.

1469
01:16:11,000 --> 01:16:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dvije godine i po.

1470
01:16:13,000 --> 01:16:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ta sam završila osnovnu školu kod časni sestara,

1471
01:16:17,000 --> 01:16:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali nisam mogla...

1472
01:16:19,000 --> 01:16:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Otac me nije dao upisati kod njih u građansku školu,

1473
01:16:23,000 --> 01:16:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] nego u gimnaziju.

1474
01:16:26,000 --> 01:16:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] da je to časno sestara.

1475
01:16:27,000 --> 01:16:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] O, ne.

1476
01:16:28,000 --> 01:16:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti česno sestra, ne.

1477
01:16:30,000 --> 01:16:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti ćeš ići u gimnaziju.

1478
01:16:32,000 --> 01:16:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Realna gimnazija je bila u Požegi.

1479
01:16:34,000 --> 01:16:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ićeš u gimnaziju.

1480
01:16:36,000 --> 01:16:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad završiš gimnaziju,

1481
01:16:38,000 --> 01:16:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] tata će te poslati u Zagreb na sve učilište

1482
01:16:41,000 --> 01:16:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] za matematiku.

1483
01:16:43,000 --> 01:16:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam znala što je sve učilište.

1484
01:16:46,000 --> 01:16:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Posli sam doznala da je univerz.

1485
01:16:51,000 --> 01:16:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

1486
01:16:52,000 --> 01:16:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad upisali me, moram ići.

1487
01:16:55,000 --> 01:16:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja sam dobro prihvatila,

1488
01:16:57,000 --> 01:16:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja ću ipak biti časna sestra.

1489
01:16:59,000 --> 01:17:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je to bila da ja ću slušati tatu.

1490
01:17:02,000 --> 01:17:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Završit ću sve što on hoće,

1491
01:17:04,000 --> 01:17:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja ću ići časne sestre.

1492
01:17:06,000 --> 01:17:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja sad ću šutiti,

1493
01:17:08,000 --> 01:17:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] neću više govoriti.

1494
01:17:10,000 --> 01:17:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ja nisam više govorila

1495
01:17:12,000 --> 01:17:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] da ću biti časna sestra

1496
01:17:14,000 --> 01:17:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] i u gimnaziju.

1497
01:17:17,000 --> 01:17:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nažalost, malo smo bili jer poslije je nastalo opet.

1498
01:17:21,000 --> 01:17:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Napadali su nas partizani, pa ih jedan put upali u grad.

1499
01:17:25,000 --> 01:17:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, bili smo skoro mjesec dana pod partizanima.

1500
01:17:29,000 --> 01:17:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali smo nastavili školu.

1501
01:17:32,000 --> 01:17:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sjećam se od naš direktor Prijašnji.

1502
01:17:34,000 --> 01:17:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] O njega su odmah slislili.

1503
01:17:36,000 --> 01:17:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, nije više direktor,

1504
01:17:39,000 --> 01:17:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] nego je bio jedan partizan.

1505
01:17:41,000 --> 01:17:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je bojnik neki.

1506
01:17:43,000 --> 01:17:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, prije smo imali njemački,

1507
01:17:46,000 --> 01:17:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] kao strani jezik.

1508
01:17:48,000 --> 01:17:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odmah su uveli ruski jezik.

1509
01:17:52,000 --> 01:17:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ponjemaš ruski."

1510
01:17:54,000 --> 01:17:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ponjemaš."

1511
01:17:56,000 --> 01:17:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, dobro.

1512
01:17:58,000 --> 01:18:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam rekla mami, ja neću učiti ruski.

1513
01:18:00,000 --> 01:18:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moraš učiti, inače će ti tatu ubit, ako nećeš učiti.

1514
01:18:03,000 --> 01:18:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sam morala učiti ruski.

1515
01:18:05,000 --> 01:18:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

1516
01:18:07,000 --> 01:18:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, jednog dana

1517
01:18:09,000 --> 01:18:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] dođeše kamiljoni

1518
01:18:12,000 --> 01:18:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] pred gimnaziju

1519
01:18:14,000 --> 01:18:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] i strpaš te naš sve u kamione.

1520
01:18:18,000 --> 01:18:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na jedno polje čupa trepu.

1521
01:18:22,000 --> 01:18:23,000
[UNKNOWN] Radna akcija.

1522
01:18:23,000 --> 01:18:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa mi djeca u cipelicama, gradskim cipelicama,

1523
01:18:27,000 --> 01:18:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] a u Slavoni je Bog dao blata koliko hoćeš.

1524
01:18:32,000 --> 01:18:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] I mi po onom blatu idemo čupat trepu.

1525
01:18:36,000 --> 01:18:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Cijeli dan.

1526
01:18:38,000 --> 01:18:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bez jest.

1527
01:18:40,000 --> 01:18:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na večer došli smo, vratili smo se kuće.

1528
01:18:43,000 --> 01:18:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala Bog da ste nas vratili kuće.

1529
01:18:45,000 --> 01:18:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sigurno bili smo, dakle, gladni.

1530
01:18:48,000 --> 01:18:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda prljavi.

1531
01:18:51,000 --> 01:18:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] da Bog čuva.

1532
01:18:52,000 --> 01:18:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ej, mom tati, baš ti nije to bilo povolje.

1533
01:18:55,000 --> 01:18:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mhm.

1534
01:18:57,000 --> 01:19:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kupiš ti jesu, možeš, ko zna kod ih možeš odvesti?

1535
01:19:01,000 --> 01:19:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da se možda upaditi.

1536
01:19:02,000 --> 01:19:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako.

1537
01:19:05,000 --> 01:19:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] opet upadeše naši...

1538
01:19:07,000 --> 01:19:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] A šta se događalo prije...

1539
01:19:12,000 --> 01:19:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] A kad su oni opobjegli partizani, onda...

1540
01:19:16,000 --> 01:19:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mi smo imeli kuću na Valerovcu.

1541
01:19:21,000 --> 01:19:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] jedan mali brežuljak, možda kilometar i pol od središta grada.

1542
01:19:24,000 --> 01:19:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, jednu večer, kuca neko na naša vrata oko polnoći.

1543
01:19:32,000 --> 01:19:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] mama otvori partizan koji je prije bio Ustaša, sad u partizanskoj odori.

1544
01:19:40,000 --> 01:19:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] I pita: "Gdje je Naca, moja sestra?"

1545
01:19:45,000 --> 01:19:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Po sreći Božem providnosti, Naca je bila kod naše kume.

1546
01:19:50,000 --> 01:19:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] A naša kum i kuma, oni su imali dvije trgovine.

1547
01:19:54,000 --> 01:19:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedne mješovite robe, a jednu za pića vojnika.

1548
01:19:59,000 --> 01:20:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad moja sestra njoj pomagala, jer su od našega kuma

1549
01:20:05,000 --> 01:20:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] odveli partizani sa sobom u pakup, u šumu.

1550
01:20:09,000 --> 01:20:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je kuma ostala sama.

1551
01:20:11,000 --> 01:20:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] A kuma je bila porijeklom talijanka.

1552
01:20:15,000 --> 01:20:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, a ona je nas jako volila.

1553
01:20:17,000 --> 01:20:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, koji put ona bi ne mogla spavat sama,

1554
01:20:21,000 --> 01:20:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] pa bi rekla moje mami: "Pošalj mi katicu da spava sama."

1555
01:20:25,000 --> 01:20:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam više puta išla spavat s njom.

1556
01:20:28,000 --> 01:20:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ona imala spavač u sobu blizu trgovine.

1557
01:20:33,000 --> 01:20:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ona bila sigurno muža, su joj otjele odakle u partizani.

1558
01:20:38,000 --> 01:20:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ima trgovinu, kuća je dosta velika.

1559
01:20:42,000 --> 01:20:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona bi se znala po noći dignuti, hodati, gledati, da li je sve u redu.

1560
01:20:46,000 --> 01:20:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja bi spavala. Onda kad bi se vratila, onda bi mene zagrla i poljubila.

1561
01:20:50,000 --> 01:20:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja bi se premila, šta je to sad?

1562
01:20:53,000 --> 01:20:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prešla i prestrašila se.

1563
01:20:55,000 --> 01:21:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Eta, onda sam jej rekla: "Mama, ja ne volim ići kumi, ona mene po noći grli."

1564
01:21:01,000 --> 01:21:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je sestra morala ići.

1565
01:21:05,000 --> 01:21:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda, od više puta onda je sestra išla.

1566
01:21:09,000 --> 01:21:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tada, hvala Bogu, bila je sestra.

1567
01:21:12,000 --> 01:21:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam mama odmah utro poslala: "Idi reci da se ne vraća kuć."

1568
01:21:17,000 --> 01:21:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer opasnost je, ovaj dolazi.

1569
01:21:20,000 --> 01:21:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je bio Ustaša, on se u nju zaljubio.

1570
01:21:24,000 --> 01:21:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad hetio je da je uzme išao u partizane.

1571
01:21:29,000 --> 01:21:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Po sreći ona je bila u gradu.

1572
01:21:31,000 --> 01:21:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je odmah Ohona otišla iz Požege

1573
01:21:34,000 --> 01:21:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] sa jednim našim rođakom koji je bio domobran.

1574
01:21:38,000 --> 01:21:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer je bilo isto i domobranska armija je bila.

1575
01:21:41,000 --> 01:21:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ona je otišla mojoj sestri koja živjela u Jasenovcu.

1576
01:21:46,000 --> 01:21:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je išla k njoj u Jasenovac.

1577
01:21:49,000 --> 01:21:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Isto tako i brat Marko.

1578
01:21:51,000 --> 01:21:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su se odmah makli.

1579
01:21:53,000 --> 01:21:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sam ja sama ostala s tatom, mamom i stricom i tetom.

1580
01:21:57,000 --> 01:22:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer moja teta, onaj njegovog muža su ubili četnici.

1581
01:22:01,000 --> 01:22:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ona se je vratila.

1582
01:22:03,000 --> 01:22:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je živjela blizu...

1583
01:22:06,000 --> 01:22:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čekaj, djetog, nijedno mjesto.

1584
01:22:09,000 --> 01:22:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad se ne... ta blizu drvara.

1585
01:22:12,000 --> 01:22:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je i onda je došla bez išta.

1586
01:22:16,000 --> 01:22:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Došla je k nama u Grahovo.

1587
01:22:18,000 --> 01:22:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tata je rekao: "Ti ostani s nama. Šta nama? To i tebi."

1588
01:22:22,000 --> 01:22:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ona je bila uvijek s nama poslije.

1589
01:22:26,000 --> 01:22:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Radila je. Tato je rekao: "Što zaradiš, drži za se. S nama ćeš jesti, pitis..."

1590
01:22:32,000 --> 01:22:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je. Moj otac je bio jako dareživ.

1591
01:22:36,000 --> 01:22:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Volio je svojeg sestor.

1592
01:22:38,000 --> 01:22:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mama je isto bila s njima.

1593
01:22:40,000 --> 01:22:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo joj nikad imali kakvog prepira.

1594
01:22:43,000 --> 01:22:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] U kući ja nisam doživjela slađe.

1595
01:22:46,000 --> 01:22:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ni prepira. To je jako važno u obitelji.

1596
01:22:50,000 --> 01:22:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad tata nije digao, glas na mamu ili nešto. Nikad.

1597
01:22:54,000 --> 01:22:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nikad nisam čula da je među njima nešto.

1598
01:22:57,000 --> 01:22:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam čak spavala s njima.

1599
01:22:59,000 --> 01:23:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam uvijek spavala. Kad je moja sestra Boja, udala se.

1600
01:23:04,000 --> 01:23:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se vratila i spavala uvijek s tatom i mamom.

1601
01:23:08,000 --> 01:23:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] 12 godina. Dok nismo pobjegli iz poželje.

1602
01:23:12,000 --> 01:23:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ja sam doživjela u obitelji mir, slogu, poštivanje.

1603
01:23:21,000 --> 01:23:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to mi je ostalo.

1604
01:23:24,000 --> 01:23:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] A to je jako važno.

1605
01:23:26,000 --> 01:23:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da otac i majka nikad pred djecom ne prepričeš.

1606
01:23:30,000 --> 01:23:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da si dogovore, ali da djeca ne znaju.

1607
01:23:36,000 --> 01:23:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je jako važno u obitelji.

1608
01:23:38,000 --> 01:23:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Makar ja toga nisam doživjela nikoga, svađa i prepira nikad.

1609
01:23:43,000 --> 01:23:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj stric je volio moju mamu. Ona je njega volila. Ona je ček njemu cigarete kupovala.

1610
01:23:49,000 --> 01:23:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pitala je: "Bratcu, imaš li cigareta?"

1611
01:23:52,000 --> 01:23:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ona je njemu kupovala.

1612
01:23:55,000 --> 01:24:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] U obitelji ja sam doživjela taki mir, slogu i poštovanje.

1613
01:24:00,000 --> 01:24:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to mi je ostalo.

1614
01:24:03,000 --> 01:24:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad nisam nešto rekla tete ili stricu ili tatinu Bože, sad čuvaj.

1615
01:24:08,000 --> 01:24:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije se ni smijela.

1616
01:24:10,000 --> 01:24:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ma kako je? Nisam imala razloga.

1617
01:24:14,000 --> 01:24:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam imala razloga. Tako je.

1618
01:24:16,000 --> 01:24:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je tako bilo. Kažem ja hvala Bogu da sam ja imala takvu obitelj.

1619
01:24:21,000 --> 01:24:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] To sam doživjela. I to mi je ostalo.

1620
01:24:25,000 --> 01:24:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se nikad ne sebađi iz njih. Ja ne volim se nikim svađat.

1621
01:24:28,000 --> 01:24:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako nešto rekla ja se okren, čao. Idem svojim putem.

1622
01:24:33,000 --> 01:24:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ja ne volim svađa. To meni ne paše.

1623
01:24:39,000 --> 01:24:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da moj brat Marko i Naca, oni su otišli. Tako da sam ja ostala sama.

1624
01:24:48,000 --> 01:24:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] I u jednom večer upadoše partizane u našu kuću.

1625
01:24:53,000 --> 01:24:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad jedan uleti i pita mamu špage.

1626
01:24:57,000 --> 01:25:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da mu dadne špage, da sveže jednu granatu.

1627
01:25:01,000 --> 01:25:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da bolje esplodira.

1628
01:25:04,000 --> 01:25:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad mama, mama mu dadne špagu.

1629
01:25:07,000 --> 01:25:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] On izađe van, esplodira.

1630
01:25:10,000 --> 01:25:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] A jedan drugi se svadio s mojom petom.

1631
01:25:14,000 --> 01:25:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, gdje ti je muž?

1632
01:25:16,000 --> 01:25:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, a ona njemu, ubili ga takvi kao što ste vi.

1633
01:25:21,000 --> 01:25:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mama nju gleda, mara, pa nes nešto.

1634
01:25:24,000 --> 01:25:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja sjedim kraj mame.

1635
01:25:28,000 --> 01:25:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] I slušam, moj tata sjedi, moj stric sjedi.

1636
01:25:31,000 --> 01:25:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona se s njim svađa.

1637
01:25:33,000 --> 01:25:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mama na nju gleda.

1638
01:25:35,000 --> 01:25:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pazi, imaš bratčuk.

1639
01:25:38,000 --> 01:25:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Brata svoje obada.

1640
01:25:40,000 --> 01:25:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa taj stric.

1641
01:25:42,000 --> 01:25:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imaš, mama, pa šta je njemu za...

1642
01:25:46,000 --> 01:25:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Eliminirati se u momentu.

1643
01:25:48,000 --> 01:25:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, i ti ćeš završiti.

1644
01:25:51,000 --> 01:25:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on iziđe, granasta iz grade njega da pogodi u sto komada je otišao.

1645
01:25:58,000 --> 01:26:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] A obećao da će nas ponoviti.

1646
01:26:03,000 --> 01:26:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem ti, sad ti vidi tu Božju providnost.

1647
01:26:07,000 --> 01:26:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Božju zaštitu.

1648
01:26:10,000 --> 01:26:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je njemu iskreno rekla, joj je došlo do ovlje ti partizani šta sve rade.

1649
01:26:16,000 --> 01:26:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Četnici rade, partizani rade. Pa dosta ih je više.

1650
01:26:21,000 --> 01:26:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda pobjegaš opet bili su...

1651
01:26:24,000 --> 01:26:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] U gradu su bili tada osma lovačka, to je bilo domobrani.

1652
01:26:30,000 --> 01:26:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] I bili su SS-ovci.

1653
01:26:32,000 --> 01:26:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da su istjerali opet partizane.

1654
01:26:36,000 --> 01:26:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda tata kaže: "Nama nema drugog gospasa, nego da idemo u središte grada."

1655
01:26:41,000 --> 01:26:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda zamoli časne sestre, a one su imali neke prostorije za služinčad.

1656
01:26:49,000 --> 01:26:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer su prazne.

1657
01:26:50,000 --> 01:26:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je zamoljio da bi mogle nama iznajmiti, da mi se preselimo.

1658
01:26:55,000 --> 01:26:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer nam je opasno, bili smo baš na granici našoj...

1659
01:26:58,000 --> 01:27:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na liniji.

1660
01:27:00,000 --> 01:27:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da na toj liniji, a sve smo doživjeli nebolje u Grahovu, pa ćemo još sada tu.

1661
01:27:06,000 --> 01:27:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda se mi preselimo kod časnice stara na toj njihoj prostoriji.

1662
01:27:11,000 --> 01:27:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bila nam par soba.

1663
01:27:15,000 --> 01:27:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tamo smo lijepo smjestili.

1664
01:27:21,000 --> 01:27:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo čak i jednu svinju zaklali.

1665
01:27:25,000 --> 01:27:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pripremili smo čak i, kako se zove, sapune.

1666
01:27:32,000 --> 01:27:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moja teta i mama znali su od nogu i od nekih stvari.

1667
01:27:40,000 --> 01:27:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] napravlja tablista puna i jasne ih lijepo sve složila.

1668
01:27:43,000 --> 01:27:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] I pripremili smo zimnicu i sve.

1669
01:27:46,000 --> 01:27:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad jednu večer, oko tri sata noći četvrtog prosinca, kucaju na naše prozore, mi napuštamo grad.

1670
01:28:00,000 --> 01:28:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] vojnici naši.

1671
01:28:01,000 --> 01:28:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Napuštamo grad, nemamo municije, nemamo hrane.

1672
01:28:05,000 --> 01:28:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nemamo se s čim boriti.

1673
01:28:08,000 --> 01:28:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ko želi s nama ići, idemo pješke preko požeške gore.

1674
01:28:13,000 --> 01:28:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ko ostane na milost i nemilost.

1675
01:28:19,000 --> 01:28:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] I vi ste otišli.

1676
01:28:20,000 --> 01:28:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo morali, moj brat postao vojnik, naš hrvatski vojnik, moramo ići. Nema nam spasa.

1677
01:28:30,000 --> 01:28:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda nešto, ja sam neke stvari, neki koferić ili vrećice, šta smo već imali, da smo mogli nešto zasesati, šta se možemo presvući.

1678
01:28:41,000 --> 01:28:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Drugo sve ostaje.

1679
01:28:43,000 --> 01:28:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imali smo čak malu gicu, svinju, da za Božić, onda moj stric je uzeo vreću kuruze i dao je, kaže, jedi koliko hoćeš.

1680
01:28:58,000 --> 01:29:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, smo ostavili živo i tako ostavili smo opet sve.

1681
01:29:04,000 --> 01:29:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa, samo što smo se mogli presvući, tako da drugo smo se opet ostavili.

1682
01:29:12,000 --> 01:29:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, po sreći čašne sestre su imale kola, a moj tata je teško hodao jer imao probleme s nogama.

1683
01:29:22,000 --> 01:29:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on je po sreći mogao tići na kola i mama.

1684
01:29:27,000 --> 01:29:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njih dvoje častne sestre su im dozvolile da sjednu u kola, a teta i ja pješke.

1685
01:29:34,000 --> 01:29:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Preko 30 km preko Požeške gore.

1686
01:29:37,000 --> 01:29:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Cijeli dan kiša.

1687
01:29:42,000 --> 01:29:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] između častne sestre amabili, ona je sve honorabilisa Bramović, a bila je zadnju godinu moja učiteljica.

1688
01:29:53,000 --> 01:29:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] I je pater Leander, to je bilo jedan Isusovac.

1689
01:29:57,000 --> 01:30:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja između njih dvoje pješke.

1690
01:30:00,000 --> 01:30:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] I oni smo, mi smo pričali, tako hodali zajedno pješke.

1691
01:30:05,000 --> 01:30:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kiša nas spadala, okolo je bilo snijega.

1692
01:30:10,000 --> 01:30:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] prvo gradić i kapel Batrina se kvala, mokri.

1693
01:30:14,000 --> 01:30:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ljudi su nas stvarno otvarili vrata i tako.

1694
01:30:18,000 --> 01:30:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nama su napravili na sred jednog dvorišta veliku vatru.

1695
01:30:23,000 --> 01:30:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da smo se ugrijali i obsušili.

1696
01:30:26,000 --> 01:30:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo, sad ova moja, dakle dvije curice su bile,

1697
01:30:33,000 --> 01:30:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] jedna je bila, bile su Duvić, obada je.

1698
01:30:38,000 --> 01:30:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, s nama su došli isto u Požegi,

1699
01:30:42,000 --> 01:30:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] tog mače Duvića se zvao, njegove čerke.

1700
01:30:46,000 --> 01:30:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] One su otišle u kolegiji, časnim sestrama.

1701
01:30:52,000 --> 01:30:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mama je umrla, baka umrla i sad tata sam.

1702
01:30:57,000 --> 01:31:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ih je stavio u kolegiji, kod časnice stara imali su one kolegiju.

1703
01:31:03,000 --> 01:31:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] U zavod, časnim se starao.

1704
01:31:05,000 --> 01:31:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja sam isto htjela ići, tata.

1705
01:31:07,000 --> 01:31:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ti nećeš u zavod.

1706
01:31:09,000 --> 01:31:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti nećeš u zavod.

1707
01:31:11,000 --> 01:31:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] A meni je, ja bi raza ušla, sestrama ta.

1708
01:31:14,000 --> 01:31:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ja nisam.

1709
01:31:16,000 --> 01:31:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako kad su one izišle poverine, onda smo se sustreli u kapel Batrini.

1710
01:31:20,000 --> 01:31:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad jedna od njih mlađa, Tom, kad se zvala,

1711
01:31:23,000 --> 01:31:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] cipele su raspale.

1712
01:31:26,000 --> 01:31:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] A imala samo jedan par cipela.

1713
01:31:28,000 --> 01:31:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja po sreći sam uzela tri para cipela.

1714
01:31:32,000 --> 01:31:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sam jedan njoj dala.

1715
01:31:34,000 --> 01:31:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uzmi koji hoćeš.

1716
01:31:35,000 --> 01:31:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da jedan par cipele, ona uzela.

1717
01:31:39,000 --> 01:31:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] I dva kaputa sam imala.

1718
01:31:41,000 --> 01:31:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde, uzmi jedan kaput.

1719
01:31:42,000 --> 01:31:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sam imala što se imala razdijela.

1720
01:31:45,000 --> 01:31:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što ste imali, dali ste.

1721
01:31:46,000 --> 01:31:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je tako.

1722
01:31:48,000 --> 01:31:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad nema nikom, moraš pomoć.

1723
01:31:50,000 --> 01:31:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je situacija.

1724
01:31:52,000 --> 01:31:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo došli u kapel Batrini.

1725
01:31:55,000 --> 01:32:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj brat je saznao da ljudi izlaze iz Požege.

1726
01:32:00,000 --> 01:32:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on je služio u Orjevcu.

1727
01:32:04,000 --> 01:32:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je došao s kolima s jednim sedljakom po nas.

1728
01:32:13,000 --> 01:32:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Drugi su išli u Novu gradešku.

1729
01:32:17,000 --> 01:32:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Drugi su proslijedili.

1730
01:32:19,000 --> 01:32:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je nas uzeo i odneo u Orjevac.

1731
01:32:23,000 --> 01:32:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda smo bili u nastavbi s vojnicima.

1732
01:32:25,000 --> 01:32:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Teta, mama i ja smo spavali u redu.

1733
01:32:29,000 --> 01:32:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jednog od našeg Sarića koji je bio glavnim.

1734
01:32:33,000 --> 01:32:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] On nam je dao, a tata i stric s vojnicima u nastavbi.

1735
01:32:37,000 --> 01:32:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo smo jedno desetak dana.

1736
01:32:40,000 --> 01:32:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sigurno ne možemo biti sad s vojnicima.

1737
01:32:42,000 --> 01:32:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda čim bi, recimo, avione nalazli, ja bi plakala.

1738
01:32:46,000 --> 01:32:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer sam se u Požegi, bila bi uzbuno.

1739
01:32:49,000 --> 01:32:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bi plakala.

1740
01:32:52,000 --> 01:32:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] To znaš što je strah.

1741
01:32:53,000 --> 01:32:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Stres koji se doživio.

1742
01:32:55,000 --> 01:32:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Stresu.

1743
01:32:57,000 --> 01:32:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda, onda, vojnici bih:

1744
01:32:58,000 --> 01:33:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ne seko, nemoj plakati, neće nam biti ništa."

1745
01:33:01,000 --> 01:33:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] A stambajte?

1746
01:33:03,000 --> 01:33:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] To znaju da su vojnici tu.

1747
01:33:05,000 --> 01:33:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mogu slobodno pucat i bacat bombe.

1748
01:33:08,000 --> 01:33:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako.

1749
01:33:09,000 --> 01:33:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda smo...

1750
01:33:11,000 --> 01:33:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vrat je bilo, šta?

1751
01:33:13,000 --> 01:33:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Najbolje kaža da idete u Jasenovac.

1752
01:33:16,000 --> 01:33:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo je moja sestra bila s djecom.

1753
01:33:18,000 --> 01:33:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda smo otišli.

1754
01:33:21,000 --> 01:33:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] sa jednom grupom vojnika, talijanski vojnika u jednom kamionu.

1755
01:33:25,000 --> 01:33:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo su odjeli do Jasenovca.

1756
01:33:27,000 --> 01:33:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda tamo su bili u Jasenovcu.

1757
01:33:29,000 --> 01:33:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Božićevali smo.

1758
01:33:31,000 --> 01:33:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odmah za Božića.

1759
01:33:34,000 --> 01:33:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan vi bombardirani u Novsku.

1760
01:33:37,000 --> 01:33:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan je bilo.

1761
01:33:39,000 --> 01:33:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] U Novsku su se, ja mislim, sve uništili.

1762
01:33:43,000 --> 01:33:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda kažem, najbolje da idemo...

1763
01:33:45,000 --> 01:33:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj otac je rekao, najbolje da videte za Austriju.

1764
01:33:49,000 --> 01:33:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovdje više nema mira.

1765
01:33:51,000 --> 01:33:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi ćemo ostati u Hrvatskoj.

1766
01:33:54,000 --> 01:33:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Stric, tata, mama i braća.

1767
01:33:58,000 --> 01:34:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] A vi idete tamo, će biti sigurnije.

1768
01:34:01,000 --> 01:34:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bili su transporti.

1769
01:34:04,000 --> 01:34:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kad smo uzeli, bilo je dosta naroda.

1770
01:34:09,000 --> 01:34:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čito, Foksdovićeri su išli.

1771
01:34:11,000 --> 01:34:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su bježali.

1772
01:34:13,000 --> 01:34:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, bježali su.

1773
01:34:14,000 --> 01:34:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda i mi smo s njima.

1774
01:34:15,000 --> 01:34:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, smo došli do Zagreba.

1775
01:34:19,000 --> 01:34:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, moj otac je nas pratio.

1776
01:34:22,000 --> 01:34:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer trebao je ići na ministarstvo unutarnjih poslova

1777
01:34:27,000 --> 01:34:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] da mu isplete.

1778
01:34:29,000 --> 01:34:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, mjesec i dva, ali nisam su mu isplatili novac.

1779
01:34:31,000 --> 01:34:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je ti kaže, ja idem dignuti novac

1780
01:34:34,000 --> 01:34:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] i kupit ću malo i još jedan kaput.

1781
01:34:38,000 --> 01:34:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] i cipeli si još tako.

1782
01:34:40,000 --> 01:34:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj otac je otišao.

1783
01:34:42,000 --> 01:34:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Lak krenuo i mi ga nismo više vidjeli.

1784
01:34:46,000 --> 01:34:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, ja tatu nisam ni pozdravila.

1785
01:34:49,000 --> 01:34:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer su mi rekli, idi napuniti flašu vode.

1786
01:34:52,000 --> 01:34:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam išla napuniti flašu vode na pipu.

1787
01:34:55,000 --> 01:34:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tata je otišao.

1788
01:34:57,000 --> 01:34:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ga nisam ni pozdravila.

1789
01:34:58,000 --> 01:35:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikada ga više nisam vidjela.

1790
01:35:01,000 --> 01:35:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je bio zadnji put.

1791
01:35:02,000 --> 01:35:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zadnji put je to bio.

1792
01:35:03,000 --> 01:35:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je da je tata,

1793
01:35:06,000 --> 01:35:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad je došao na kolodvor,

1794
01:35:08,000 --> 01:35:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] nije nas našao vlake od Jurije.

1795
01:35:10,000 --> 01:35:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer se niznali rasporedi.

1796
01:35:13,000 --> 01:35:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ovi su minirali vlakove i pruge.

1797
01:35:18,000 --> 01:35:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] nisu se znali kada.

1798
01:35:19,000 --> 01:35:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da su iskoristavali vrijeme

1799
01:35:21,000 --> 01:35:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad možemo pobjeć.

1800
01:35:23,000 --> 01:35:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo

1801
01:35:25,000 --> 01:35:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] došli 20. sječnja

1802
01:35:28,000 --> 01:35:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] u Braunovu.

1803
01:35:30,000 --> 01:35:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] U logor za izbjegnice.

1804
01:35:32,000 --> 01:35:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako to su bile barake niske.

1805
01:35:35,000 --> 01:35:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo se mogli ispraviti samo tu.

1806
01:35:38,000 --> 01:35:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] U središtu.

1807
01:35:40,000 --> 01:35:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] u središtu.

1808
01:35:41,000 --> 01:35:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek smo u Radu.

1809
01:35:42,000 --> 01:35:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sa strane su bile daske gdje smo mogli sjesti ili ležati.

1810
01:35:46,000 --> 01:35:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] I koliko je naših ljudi bilo u logoru?

1811
01:35:51,000 --> 01:35:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] U našem logoru je bilo oko 200, 220.

1812
01:35:55,000 --> 01:35:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo smo samo žene i djeca.

1813
01:35:57,000 --> 01:35:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] S nama je bio

1814
01:35:58,000 --> 01:36:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] svećenik.

1815
01:36:00,000 --> 01:36:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Praoslav svećenik Hrvat.

1816
01:36:03,000 --> 01:36:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je praoslavni vjere.

1817
01:36:06,000 --> 01:36:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je bio s nama njegova supruga i sin.

1818
01:36:10,000 --> 01:36:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je bio u našem logoru.

1819
01:36:13,000 --> 01:36:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je jako jedna fina osoba.

1820
01:36:15,000 --> 01:36:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pravi Hrvat.

1821
01:36:17,000 --> 01:36:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je te vjere i mi smo ga poštivali.

1822
01:36:20,000 --> 01:36:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on je išao u našu crkvu.

1823
01:36:23,000 --> 01:36:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je gospod Proto.

1824
01:36:25,000 --> 01:36:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Smo ga zvali.

1825
01:36:26,000 --> 01:36:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gospod Proto, gospođa.

1826
01:36:28,000 --> 01:36:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] I Nela, Nela, Nenad je bio sin.

1827
01:36:30,000 --> 01:36:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Starim se zvao.

1828
01:36:31,000 --> 01:36:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da nas je bilo...

1829
01:36:33,000 --> 01:36:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo se slagali u Tvom grau.

1830
01:36:37,000 --> 01:36:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Najkirchen je naš bio logor.

1831
01:36:40,000 --> 01:36:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo uklad šume.

1832
01:36:43,000 --> 01:36:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pak uz šumu.

1833
01:36:45,000 --> 01:36:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo mi...

1834
01:36:47,000 --> 01:36:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bili tu od...

1835
01:36:51,000 --> 01:36:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] jedno verimestim dolg skorom aprila.

1836
01:36:56,000 --> 01:37:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je nastala velika kiša i unišle su vode u marake.

1837
01:37:03,000 --> 01:37:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo...

1838
01:37:05,000 --> 01:37:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su nas preneli u jedan dio, u jedan hotel, u stredištu mjesta.

1839
01:37:12,000 --> 01:37:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je Mali Gradić bio.

1840
01:37:14,000 --> 01:37:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] A jedan dio u školu.

1841
01:37:16,000 --> 01:37:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tamo smo bili oko mjesec dana u sali za ples.

1842
01:37:21,000 --> 01:37:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo stigli.

1843
01:37:24,000 --> 01:37:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] U nas je šestdeset osoba.

1844
01:37:26,000 --> 01:37:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dan i noć.

1845
01:37:28,000 --> 01:37:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tu smo spavali, tu smo jeli, tu smo...

1846
01:37:32,000 --> 01:37:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, nikad kve svađaje nikad nije bilo.

1847
01:37:37,000 --> 01:37:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] A kakvi su bili ostali uvjeti?

1848
01:37:39,000 --> 01:37:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da li ste imali higijenske uvjete?

1849
01:37:40,000 --> 01:37:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da li ste imali dovoljno hrana?

1850
01:37:42,000 --> 01:37:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Higijenski imali smo samo par...

1851
01:37:43,000 --> 01:37:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je par zahoda dolje.

1852
01:37:45,000 --> 01:37:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mhm.

1853
01:37:46,000 --> 01:37:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Drugo ne.

1854
01:37:48,000 --> 01:37:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa se mogao, ništa oprat.

1855
01:37:49,000 --> 01:37:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tako ste živjeli?

1856
01:37:52,000 --> 01:37:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi skupa u jednoj prostoriji?

1857
01:37:54,000 --> 01:37:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ha, ne možeš se presući, ne možeš se oprati.

1858
01:37:58,000 --> 01:37:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je, kažem ti.

1859
01:37:59,000 --> 01:38:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali niko se nije razbolio.

1860
01:38:00,000 --> 01:38:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kažem ti to.

1861
01:38:04,000 --> 01:38:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Božja...

1862
01:38:06,000 --> 01:38:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Božja milost.

1863
01:38:07,000 --> 01:38:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Božja milost.

1864
01:38:08,000 --> 01:38:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem ti.

1865
01:38:09,000 --> 01:38:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] I niko...

1866
01:38:10,000 --> 01:38:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako smo.

1867
