[SPEAKER_01] Pa nosili smo baurima.

2081
01:44:52,000 --> 01:44:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Seljacima.

2082
01:44:53,000 --> 01:44:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da nam dadnu mlijeka.

2083
01:44:55,000 --> 01:44:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Trgovali ste tako.

2084
01:44:57,000 --> 01:44:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] To...

2085
01:44:58,000 --> 01:45:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Išli smo u šume brati toga.

2086
01:45:00,000 --> 01:45:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad bi nabrali...

2087
01:45:01,000 --> 01:45:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda bi imali smo...

2088
01:45:03,000 --> 01:45:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako od pleha neke posude.

2089
01:45:05,000 --> 01:45:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to bi odnijeli.

2090
01:45:06,000 --> 01:45:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] I molili bi...

2091
01:45:07,000 --> 01:45:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prada...

2092
01:45:08,000 --> 01:45:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Verkaufen.

2093
01:45:09,000 --> 01:45:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zamijenivali bi mlijeko za...

2094
01:45:12,000 --> 01:45:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer moja sestra imala troje djece.

2095
01:45:15,000 --> 01:45:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedno malo se rodilo.

2096
01:45:17,000 --> 01:45:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mala Anđela.

2097
01:45:18,000 --> 01:45:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Se rodila.

2098
01:45:19,000 --> 01:45:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] I dva sina, Marko i Andrija.

2099
01:45:23,000 --> 01:45:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Trebalo ih je nahraniti.

2100
01:45:25,000 --> 01:45:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da.

2101
01:45:26,000 --> 01:45:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Joj, Anđela je bila zlatna.

2102
01:45:28,000 --> 01:45:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bože moj.

2103
01:45:29,000 --> 01:45:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja volila djecu.

2104
01:45:31,000 --> 01:45:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bože sada.

2105
01:45:32,000 --> 01:45:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem...

2106
01:45:33,000 --> 01:45:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali hvala Bogu.

2107
01:45:34,000 --> 01:45:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gospođa Pađen isto imala.

2108
01:45:36,000 --> 01:45:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ova Gospođa Došen.

2109
01:45:38,000 --> 01:45:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imala je maloga.

2110
01:45:39,000 --> 01:45:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa imamo šest mjeseci.

2111
01:45:41,000 --> 01:45:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] I dugo je tri curice.

2112
01:45:43,000 --> 01:45:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, dva dvečka je imala i tri curice.

2113
01:45:46,000 --> 01:45:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Petar ih je imala.

2114
01:45:48,000 --> 01:45:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

2115
01:45:49,000 --> 01:45:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da.

2116
01:45:50,000 --> 01:45:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Puno djece u Baraci je bilo.

2117
01:45:52,000 --> 01:46:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kažem, mi smo si pomagali tako da smo mi, curice ove, išli smo brat te bobice i zamjenivali lirice za mlijeko.

2118
01:46:04,000 --> 01:46:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pravi ubitišen mirk.

2119
01:46:06,000 --> 01:46:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ona bi nama dali mlijeko presano.

2120
01:46:10,000 --> 01:46:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer oni su morali jedan dio dati u grad i drugi bi presali što ostane njima i tako.

2121
01:46:22,000 --> 01:46:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ono što, zapravo kad sve stigno, kada sve digno, ostane u nama.

2122
01:46:28,000 --> 01:46:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je ostatak je išla.

2123
01:46:29,000 --> 01:46:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je ostatak dan u nama.

2124
01:46:30,000 --> 01:46:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

2125
01:46:31,000 --> 01:46:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mi smo bili zadoljni da makar to imamo.

2126
01:46:33,000 --> 01:46:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to je bilo, da.

2127
01:46:35,000 --> 01:46:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

2128
01:46:36,000 --> 01:46:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo tako.

2129
01:46:37,000 --> 01:46:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda tu smo bili mi sve do mjeseca, dakle sedmog mjeseca ili osmog sad.

2130
01:46:47,000 --> 01:46:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, bili smo mi tu.

2131
01:46:50,000 --> 01:46:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] A posle reći, a kad je pala, dok je hrvatska, pala njemačka, grozota.

2132
01:46:57,000 --> 01:47:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] He, sad dolaj, mi smo imeli jednog hrvatskog logornika koji se brinu za naš logor.

2133
01:47:04,000 --> 01:47:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad on dođe k nama.

2134
01:47:06,000 --> 01:47:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, znate šta?

2135
01:47:08,000 --> 01:47:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pala je hrvatska, pala njemačka, grozna šta će biti s nama.

2136
01:47:13,000 --> 01:47:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, da dođe će ili amerikanci ili englezi.

2137
01:47:18,000 --> 01:47:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dao Bog da patnemo u ruke amerikanaca.

2138
01:47:23,000 --> 01:47:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ima zone su razdijeljene.

2139
01:47:25,000 --> 01:47:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ima i rusi, englezi, amerikanci.

2140
01:47:29,000 --> 01:47:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, po sreći, mi pali pod americku zonu.

2141
01:47:36,000 --> 01:47:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] I došli amerikanci vojska u logor.

2142
01:47:40,000 --> 01:47:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] O, nas djecu skupili na džip.

2143
01:47:43,000 --> 01:47:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Strpali li se na džip i vozali.

2144
01:47:48,000 --> 01:47:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vamo, bilo veselje.

2145
01:47:51,000 --> 01:47:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, davali nam kaugume.

2146
01:47:55,000 --> 01:47:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odmah, svi kaugume.

2147
01:47:57,000 --> 01:48:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da moja mama išljena živcete kaugume.

2148
01:48:02,000 --> 01:48:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Inač, vozali nas.

2149
01:48:04,000 --> 01:48:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tako, i tu smo s nima.

2150
01:48:06,000 --> 01:48:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ta, recimo,

2151
01:48:08,000 --> 01:48:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] ta, kako je rekla, armija šta je bilo,

2152
01:48:12,000 --> 01:48:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] satnija, koja nas preuzela.

2153
01:48:15,000 --> 01:48:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona nas je morala posudako odvodat, kada oni idu.

2154
01:48:19,000 --> 01:48:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, vi se za njima seli.

2155
01:48:21,000 --> 01:48:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su nas preuzeli, naš logor.

2156
01:48:24,000 --> 01:48:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kud se oni reću, vode nas.

2157
01:48:27,000 --> 01:48:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sao nas trpaju na kamione.

2158
01:48:29,000 --> 01:48:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] I idete dalje.

2159
01:48:30,000 --> 01:48:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] I idemo s njima.

2160
01:48:31,000 --> 01:48:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo, u stvari, nomadski način života.

2161
01:48:34,000 --> 01:48:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Više nego...

2162
01:48:35,000 --> 01:48:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] To, da.

2163
01:48:36,000 --> 01:48:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad mi smo, recimo,

2164
01:48:37,000 --> 01:48:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad smo izišli iz Nojkirchena,

2165
01:48:39,000 --> 01:48:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] iz tih baraka,

2166
01:48:40,000 --> 01:48:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda smo išli u bolje barake.

2167
01:48:42,000 --> 01:48:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] I osazidane.

2168
01:48:44,000 --> 01:48:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Najprej smo išli u Ranzhofen.

2169
01:48:48,000 --> 01:48:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] U Ranzhofenu smo bili par mjeseci.

2170
01:48:52,000 --> 01:48:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Par mjeseci.

2171
01:48:53,000 --> 01:48:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda iz Ranzhofena išli u Sant Johan.

2172
01:48:57,000 --> 01:49:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] U Sant Johanu već je bila zima.

2173
01:49:00,000 --> 01:49:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Snijeg. Božić.

2174
01:49:02,000 --> 01:49:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je snijega.

2175
01:49:04,000 --> 01:49:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Slik.

2176
01:49:05,000 --> 01:49:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo se išli sklizati.

2177
01:49:07,000 --> 01:49:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Djeca.

2178
01:49:09,000 --> 01:49:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Djeće radaš.

2179
01:49:10,000 --> 01:49:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da ćeš drugo.

2180
01:49:11,000 --> 01:49:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, išli sklizati.

2181
01:49:12,000 --> 01:49:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na čemu?

2182
01:49:13,000 --> 01:49:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na Kaputinom.

2183
01:49:15,000 --> 01:49:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta nađeš?

2184
01:49:17,000 --> 01:49:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nađeš?

2185
01:49:18,000 --> 01:49:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tako da...

2186
01:49:19,000 --> 01:49:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tamo su došli jedna partizanska...

2187
01:49:23,000 --> 01:49:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imali smo tamo za logornika jednog Amerikanca.

2188
01:49:28,000 --> 01:49:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] A njega je zamenivao ovaj gospod Proto.

2189
01:49:31,000 --> 01:49:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Cez svećenik.

2190
01:49:32,000 --> 01:49:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je uvijek bio u našom logoru.

2191
01:49:34,000 --> 01:49:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kada jednog dana naš logornik je bio izvan, išao na ulov.

2192
01:49:41,000 --> 01:49:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

2193
01:49:42,000 --> 01:49:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ostaje samo gospod Proto da pazi na logor.

2194
01:49:46,000 --> 01:49:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] I dođoše partizani.

2195
01:49:48,000 --> 01:49:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] A auto partizanski sa crvenom zvijezdom.

2196
01:49:52,000 --> 01:49:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad hoće govorit naravno.

2197
01:49:54,000 --> 01:49:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pozovu gospod Proto.

2198
01:49:56,000 --> 01:49:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gospod Proto kaže:

2199
01:49:58,000 --> 01:49:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Iđimo da vidimo.

2200
01:49:59,000 --> 01:50:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] A jedna gospođa Kenđelić.

2201
01:50:01,000 --> 01:50:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gospođa Kenđelić je bila iz Zagreba.

2202
01:50:03,000 --> 01:50:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona nas pozove curice.

2203
01:50:05,000 --> 01:50:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] A jedna baraka je bila na visini.

2204
01:50:08,000 --> 01:50:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] A dolje oni su bili kao malo dolinica.

2205
01:50:12,000 --> 01:50:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad oni dolje.

2206
01:50:14,000 --> 01:50:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mi gore na visini.

2207
01:50:15,000 --> 01:50:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nasljeno desetak curica sa gospodom Kenđelić.

2208
01:50:21,000 --> 01:50:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad oni kode da se vratimo kući.

2209
01:50:25,000 --> 01:50:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] A mi zapijemo:

2210
01:50:27,000 --> 01:50:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Još Hrvatska ni propala dok mi živimo.

2211
01:50:31,000 --> 01:50:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Visoko se budestan.

2212
01:50:33,000 --> 01:50:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dok ju zbudimo.

2213
01:50:35,000 --> 01:50:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] I pijemo.

2214
01:50:37,000 --> 01:50:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] A dečki uzmo blatu i sad lijepe crvenu zvijezdu.

2215
01:50:42,000 --> 01:50:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da se ne vidi.

2216
01:50:44,000 --> 01:50:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] I oni odoše.

2217
01:50:46,000 --> 01:50:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali su nas imali na listi.

2218
01:50:48,000 --> 01:50:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koje god bio u našom logoru,

2219
01:50:51,000 --> 01:50:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] jao njemo ako bi se vratio kuće.

2220
01:50:54,000 --> 01:50:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] I smo ih tako istjerali iz logora.

2221
01:50:58,000 --> 01:51:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] a mi dječi podjarili.

2222
01:51:02,000 --> 01:51:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda oni odšli.

2223
01:51:06,000 --> 01:51:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Amerikanci su strogi.

2224
01:51:11,000 --> 01:51:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni ne smiju doći gdje su Amerikanci.

2225
01:51:15,000 --> 01:51:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da iz toga logora išli smo posle u Braunaugu.

2226
01:51:21,000 --> 01:51:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je mjesto gdje se rodio Hitler.

2227
01:51:26,000 --> 01:51:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] I u tom mjestu je bila isto jedan logor.

2228
01:51:31,000 --> 01:51:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo smo čak otvorili zabavište.

2229
01:51:34,000 --> 01:51:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] i gospođa Kenđelić, ona je bila učiteljica, ona je rekla:

2230
01:51:38,000 --> 01:51:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Slušaj, ti seka pađen, vi ćete meni pomagati u zabavištu."

2231
01:51:44,000 --> 01:51:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo u nas dije pomagale u zabavištu.

2232
01:51:47,000 --> 01:51:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali tamo je kratko vori.

2233
01:51:49,000 --> 01:51:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tamo je došla gospođa Amerikanca.

2234
01:51:52,000 --> 01:51:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Sisita" se zvala.

2235
01:51:54,000 --> 01:51:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je nas jako štitila.

2236
01:51:58,000 --> 01:52:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ona je nama puno pomagala.

2237
01:52:01,000 --> 01:52:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Došla je, govorila je, mislim, bio je s njom ovaj naš logornik.

2238
01:52:11,000 --> 01:52:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prevađao je, ona je govorila engleski.

2239
01:52:14,000 --> 01:52:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona nam je puno pomagala.

2240
01:52:16,000 --> 01:52:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tada smo mi počeli dobivati pakete iz Amerike.

2241
01:52:21,000 --> 01:52:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo u paketima.

2242
01:52:23,000 --> 01:52:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo smo bili dulje vremena.

2243
01:52:26,000 --> 01:52:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] I moja se sestra teško razbolila.

2244
01:52:29,000 --> 01:52:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle je bio jedan liječnik u logoru.

2245
01:52:32,000 --> 01:52:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je rekao:

2246
01:52:34,000 --> 01:52:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] "To je velika opasnost za sušicu za tibići."

2247
01:52:40,000 --> 01:52:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Najbolje je da se hrani.

2248
01:52:44,000 --> 01:52:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da dobro hranu ima i da drugoga spasa nema.

2249
01:52:49,000 --> 01:52:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Treba pijuti puno jaja."

2250
01:52:52,000 --> 01:52:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad mama kaže:

2251
01:52:54,000 --> 01:52:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Trebaš imat, tražiti jaja, kupovati jaja."

2252
01:52:57,000 --> 01:52:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Kako ćemo kupiti?"

2253
01:52:58,000 --> 01:53:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ništa, imamo cigareta, imamo čokolade."

2254
01:53:02,000 --> 01:53:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] "A ja, čokoladu."

2255
01:53:05,000 --> 01:53:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] "A ništa."

2256
01:53:07,000 --> 01:53:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Cokolada vam je bila najdraža."

2257
01:53:09,000 --> 01:53:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ništa, kažem."

2258
01:53:11,000 --> 01:53:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ja skupim tu čokoladu, cigarete."

2259
01:53:15,000 --> 01:53:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Jezna djevojka, starija malo od mene, par godina starija od mene."

2260
01:53:21,000 --> 01:53:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] "I hajdemo mi u potragu za jajima."

2261
01:53:24,000 --> 01:53:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Idemo kupovati jaja."

2262
01:53:26,000 --> 01:53:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Cijeli dan smo mi hodali."

2263
01:53:29,000 --> 01:53:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] "A bauri su, toj seljaci, jako daleko jedan od drugoga."

2264
01:53:33,000 --> 01:53:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Jer imaju njihova imanja."

2265
01:53:35,000 --> 01:53:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Cijeli dan smo."

2266
01:53:37,000 --> 01:53:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Sjećam se, to smo išli u jednom bauru, jednom seljaku."

2267
01:53:42,000 --> 01:53:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Baš si je bio ručak."

2268
01:53:44,000 --> 01:53:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] "A oni su imali neke kifle."

2269
01:53:48,000 --> 01:53:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Buhtle."

2270
01:53:51,000 --> 01:53:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] "I ona nam je dala stakove po jednom buhtlu."

2271
01:53:55,000 --> 01:54:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Bilo su tako fine, da nikad u životu nisam taki buhtle."

2272
01:54:01,000 --> 01:54:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Zapamtili ste te buhtle."

2273
01:54:03,000 --> 01:54:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Tako fine su bile, da je nešto nevjerojatno."

2274
01:54:06,000 --> 01:54:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] "I dobro."

2275
01:54:07,000 --> 01:54:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] "I ona nam je dala nekoliko jaja."

2276
01:54:09,000 --> 01:54:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ja su me dala sad ne znam, ili cigarete, šta je htjela."

2277
01:54:12,000 --> 01:54:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ili cigarete ili čokolade."

2278
01:54:14,000 --> 01:54:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Tako da sam ja skupila dvadeset jaja."

2279
01:54:17,000 --> 01:54:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] "I došla kući, a umorna."

2280
01:54:21,000 --> 01:54:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Jedva su me noge držali."

2281
01:54:23,000 --> 01:54:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Cijeli dan sam hodala."

2282
01:54:25,000 --> 01:54:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Tako da, moja teta je pravila šato, šičer."

2283
01:54:30,000 --> 01:54:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] "I svaki dan."

2284
01:54:32,000 --> 01:54:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] "I ona se oporavila, tako da nije dobila sušića."

2285
01:54:35,000 --> 01:54:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Pok, hvala."

2286
01:54:36,000 --> 01:54:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Pok, hvala."

2287
01:54:37,000 --> 01:54:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Tako da, svladala, mislim to."

2288
01:54:39,000 --> 01:54:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Jer vidi se, slaba hrana, čaj iz hrana, hladno, svašta, bjeda."

2289
01:54:46,000 --> 01:54:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Sloše uvijek."

2290
01:54:47,000 --> 01:54:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Možeš soprat, nemaš sva bjeda posvuda."

2291
01:54:50,000 --> 01:54:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Lako ti je dobiti sušiću tada."

2292
01:54:53,000 --> 01:55:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Tako da smo iz tog logora poslije išli smo, mislim, u Hasten."

2293
01:55:02,000 --> 01:55:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Tamo nas je bilo tisuće."

2294
01:55:04,000 --> 01:55:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Tamo nas je bilo svih narodnosti."

2295
01:55:07,000 --> 01:55:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Serba, Hrvata, Poljaka, Ukrajinaca."

2296
01:55:11,000 --> 01:55:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ma svake vrste."

2297
01:55:13,000 --> 01:55:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Tamo smo dosta dugo bili i tamo smo otvorili školu i srednju školu."

2298
01:55:22,000 --> 01:55:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Tada sam ja, nastavili smo jednu vrstu gimnazije."

2299
01:55:27,000 --> 01:55:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Trajala je par mjeseci."

2300
01:55:30,000 --> 01:55:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Bili smo mnomadi smo bili."

2301
01:55:33,000 --> 01:55:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ali dobro, da završili smo nešto."

2302
01:55:36,000 --> 01:55:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Engleski smo imali, dakle, naš razred."

2303
01:55:40,000 --> 01:55:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Bilo je nama s nama, je bila samo jedna Slovenka."

2304
01:55:44,000 --> 01:55:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Drugo smo bili u Hrvati."

2305
01:55:46,000 --> 01:55:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ode tamo smo došli, ja sam došla u zadnji logor."

2306
01:55:49,000 --> 01:55:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] "To je bilo, čekaj, kako sam sad već zaboravila."

2307
01:55:54,000 --> 01:55:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Bilo, blizu linca je bio."

2308
01:55:57,000 --> 01:56:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Tamo je bio zadnji logor za me."

2309
01:56:00,000 --> 01:56:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Sad sam ga zaboravila, vidiš."

2310
01:56:03,000 --> 01:56:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Kako je?"

2311
01:56:05,000 --> 01:56:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ali ja sam se već u Astenu kad smo bili, tamo smo se krizmali."

2312
01:56:11,000 --> 01:56:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Koji nismo bili krizmani."

2313
01:56:13,000 --> 01:56:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Posledila su nam jednog srećenika da nas krizma."

2314
01:56:17,000 --> 01:56:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Pripremili smo se za krizmu."

2315
01:56:19,000 --> 01:56:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] "I tamo smo imali, tamo je došao jedan svećenik iz Rima."

2316
01:56:25,000 --> 01:56:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ko želi ići u Rim za svećenika?"

2317
01:56:30,000 --> 01:56:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda sam išao: "Zašto ne bi išla iza sestre, časne sestre?"

2318
01:56:33,000 --> 01:56:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kad se je vratio drugi put, onda je rekao:

2319
01:56:36,000 --> 01:56:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ima mjesta iza časne sestre ko hoće biti časna sestra."

2320
01:56:40,000 --> 01:56:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ova moja kolegica, sekav pađen, nas dvije se odmah upišemo.

2321
01:56:45,000 --> 01:56:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja rečem: "Mama, ja sam se upisala za Rim."

2322
01:56:48,000 --> 01:56:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Pa moj sinko, pa kućeš moj."

2323
01:56:51,000 --> 01:56:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda bila je borba s nama.

2324
01:56:53,000 --> 01:56:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nadvije smo se posle borile godinu dana.

2325
01:56:57,000 --> 01:57:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da sam ja nju uvjerila da idem za časne sestre.

2326
01:57:03,000 --> 01:57:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ne znam kdje idem. Idem samo za Rim.

2327
01:57:05,000 --> 01:57:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idem za časne sre.

2328
01:57:07,000 --> 01:57:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znam gdje ću ja biti šta."

2329
01:57:08,000 --> 01:57:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je sve neizvjesno.

2330
01:57:10,000 --> 01:57:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ima.

2331
01:57:12,000 --> 01:57:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad...

2332
01:57:13,000 --> 01:57:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sigurno ja sam...

2333
01:57:15,000 --> 01:57:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ta je bila velika borba.

2334
01:57:17,000 --> 01:57:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Navezana na mamu.

2335
01:57:19,000 --> 01:57:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tate ne ima.

2336
01:57:21,000 --> 01:57:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Braće ne zna se gdje su.

2337
01:57:22,000 --> 01:57:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja...

2338
01:57:25,000 --> 01:57:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Borba je bila u meni i s mamom.

2339
01:57:28,000 --> 01:57:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam stvarno...

2340
01:57:31,000 --> 01:57:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Težila sam zatim...

2341
01:57:32,000 --> 01:57:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Opet imala neku sumnju.

2342
01:57:34,000 --> 01:57:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] I niste htjelo joj ostaviti mamu samo.

2343
01:57:37,000 --> 01:57:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mamo ostaviti samo u nogu.

2344
01:57:39,000 --> 01:57:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ja sanjam jednu noć.

2345
01:57:42,000 --> 01:57:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uđen ja...

2346
01:57:44,000 --> 01:57:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imali smo jednu baraku kao kapela.

2347
01:57:46,000 --> 01:57:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja uniđem u baraku.

2348
01:57:48,000 --> 01:57:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na jedan put se otvori tabernakul.

2349
01:57:51,000 --> 01:57:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] I vidim pjeta di Michelangelo.

2350
01:57:55,000 --> 01:57:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Majka Božja.

2351
01:57:57,000 --> 01:58:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, Isus u krilu Majke Božje.

2352
01:58:00,000 --> 01:58:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] I vidim ovu ruku kako disi dolje.

2353
01:58:04,000 --> 01:58:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se prestrašim.

2354
01:58:06,000 --> 01:58:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ruka se diže i mene gleda.

2355
01:58:10,000 --> 01:58:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ruka...

2356
01:58:12,000 --> 01:58:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Poziva.

2357
01:58:14,000 --> 01:58:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kao da me magnet neki vuče.

2358
01:58:17,000 --> 01:58:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja idem prema oltaru i kleknem pred oltar.

2359
01:58:21,000 --> 01:58:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] I probudim se.

2360
01:58:23,000 --> 01:58:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže: "Mami.

2361
01:58:27,000 --> 01:58:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mama, ja imam taj san."

2362
01:58:30,000 --> 01:58:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači da me Isus hoće.

2363
01:58:36,000 --> 01:58:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ma, kaže: "To je sanja. Šta ti vjeruješ u sanje?"

2364
01:58:39,000 --> 01:58:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ovo, pa ono.

2365
01:58:40,000 --> 01:58:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikako, nikako uvjeriti mamu.

2366
01:58:45,000 --> 01:58:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] E nakon mjesec ipo, mama sanja nešto.

2367
01:58:48,000 --> 01:58:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mjesec ipo, dva. Sanja.

2368
01:58:51,000 --> 01:58:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže: "Nas dvije sjedimo na balkončiću pred našom kućem u Grahovo."

2369
01:58:59,000 --> 01:59:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na jedan put kaže: "Dođe jedna gospođa u bijelo obučena."

2370
01:59:04,000 --> 01:59:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] I pita mene: "Da li je to tvoja curica koja želi ići u Rim?"

2371
01:59:09,000 --> 01:59:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ta tvoja djevojčica želi u Rim."

2372
01:59:12,000 --> 01:59:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Za časnu se: "Je."

2373
01:59:14,000 --> 01:59:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] A kaže: "A tri goluba lete na naše kuće pjevaju."

2374
01:59:18,000 --> 01:59:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Pustite svakog da idu kod hoće."

2375
01:59:21,000 --> 01:59:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ono se probudi.

2376
01:59:25,000 --> 01:59:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] I zamišljenom.

2377
01:59:28,000 --> 01:59:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže: "A ona je bila jako pobozna.

2378
01:59:30,000 --> 01:59:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ta gospođa u bijelini je sigurno majka Božja."

2379
01:59:34,000 --> 01:59:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ta tri goluba to je signo presvjeto trojstvo.

2380
01:59:38,000 --> 01:59:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, ako Bog hoće,

2381
01:59:42,000 --> 01:59:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda ja nemam više snage.

2382
01:59:46,000 --> 01:59:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije se mogla to naodobri?

2383
01:59:48,000 --> 01:59:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije. Imala je vjeru čvrstvu.

2384
01:59:50,000 --> 01:59:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je to Božja bolja, onda ide.

2385
01:59:54,000 --> 01:59:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] A bilo je teško sigurno?

2386
01:59:57,000 --> 02:00:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je pet godina još ostala u logoru i mene čekala.

2387
02:00:01,000 --> 02:00:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ostalo je sama?

2388
02:00:03,000 --> 02:00:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sama. S drugim ženama.

2389
02:00:05,000 --> 02:00:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo. Mene čekala.

2390
02:00:07,000 --> 02:00:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona se je bojala da ja neću izdržati.

2391
02:00:11,000 --> 02:00:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam bila dosta razmažena.

2392
02:00:14,000 --> 02:00:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, kako ona može izdržati u samostanu, u strogosti?

2393
02:00:20,000 --> 02:00:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije vjerovala da možete.

2394
02:00:23,000 --> 02:00:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije ona, nije vjerovala.

2395
02:00:26,000 --> 02:00:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] nije trebala položiti zavijete.

2396
02:00:28,000 --> 02:00:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je došao svećenik koji je nas vodio u logoru.

2397
02:00:34,000 --> 02:00:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže: "Slušaj, ja sam došao, mama te čeka."

2398
02:00:37,000 --> 02:00:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon pet godina.

2399
02:00:39,000 --> 02:00:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mama te čeka.

2400
02:00:41,000 --> 02:00:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja sutra polažem zavijete.

2401
02:00:45,000 --> 02:00:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se ne vraćam.

2402
02:00:46,000 --> 02:00:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] I evo, sedamdeset godina nakon toga još uvijek ste ovdje.

2403
02:00:52,000 --> 02:00:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sedamdeset i tri godina ja sam redovnica.

2404
02:00:56,000 --> 02:01:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sedamdeset i tri.

2405
02:01:00,000 --> 02:01:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kažem, ja sam bila uvjerena da me Bog hoče i da me Bog vodi.

2406
02:01:06,000 --> 02:01:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja sam molila.

2407
02:01:09,000 --> 02:01:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam molila da me sveti duh prosvijeti,

2408
02:01:14,000 --> 02:01:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam ustrajem.

2409
02:01:15,000 --> 02:01:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer nije lako ustrajeti.

2410
02:01:17,000 --> 02:01:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sa mnom su bile i dosta, i druge djevojčice su došle.

2411
02:01:20,000 --> 02:01:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] A sve su napustile.

2412
02:01:22,000 --> 02:01:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam ja se vratila u Zagreb,

2413
02:01:24,000 --> 02:01:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] moj brat Ivica se zatvorio u sobu sa mnom.

2414
02:01:27,000 --> 02:01:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže: "Ti se moraš vratiti.

2415
02:01:29,000 --> 02:01:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si otišla iz nevolje, kaže u samostanu.

2416
02:01:34,000 --> 02:01:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer nisi znala kud ćeš."

2417
02:01:36,000 --> 02:01:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem: "To je moglo biti istina, Ivica.

2418
02:01:39,000 --> 02:01:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti imaš pravo."

2419
02:01:41,000 --> 02:01:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja sam imala zvanje.

2420
02:01:43,000 --> 02:01:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sa mnom su došle druge djevojčice,

2421
02:01:45,000 --> 02:01:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali nisu ostale.

2422
02:01:47,000 --> 02:01:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu umjeli pravog zvanja.

2423
02:01:49,000 --> 02:01:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da budeš svećan i redovan,

2424
02:01:52,000 --> 02:01:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] moraš imat pravo zvanje.

2425
02:01:54,000 --> 02:01:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moraš biti pozvan.

2426
02:01:56,000 --> 02:02:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer ako nisi pozvan, te baš pozvan i izabran.

2427
02:02:01,000 --> 02:02:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nema ti druge.

2428
02:02:02,000 --> 02:02:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moraš ih, koje ti je Bog dao to zvanje, drži se toga.

2429
02:02:07,000 --> 02:02:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zato kažem: "Bilo srećeničko, bilo redovničko, bilo obiteljsko, to je veliko zvanje kuda te Bog hoće."

2430
02:02:17,000 --> 02:02:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tamo radi u tom zvanju.

2431
02:02:19,000 --> 02:02:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Radi, zalaži se i ne ima ti druge.

2432
02:02:27,000 --> 02:02:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bili su i lijepi dani, i veseli, i vedri, ali bilo je i tmurni dana.

2433
02:02:33,000 --> 02:02:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je i po teškoća, ali po svakom životu je to ima.

2434
02:02:37,000 --> 02:02:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] život nije tako lagan kako mi mislimo kad smo mladi.

2435
02:02:41,000 --> 02:02:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] A život ima svakakih problema koji nisi predvidio.

2436
02:02:46,000 --> 02:02:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali trebaš imati tu hrabrost i reći: "Bože, pomozi mi. To mi je teško, ali pomozi mi."

2437
02:02:53,000 --> 02:02:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] I izdržiš.

2438
02:02:55,000 --> 02:02:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo reći da ste imali jako težak život u stvari.

2439
02:02:59,000 --> 02:03:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pogotovo prve godine vašeg života i godine rata, logora, svega toga što ste prošli.

2440
02:03:06,000 --> 02:03:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nikad izgubili nadu i vjeru?

2441
02:03:08,000 --> 02:03:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne. Ja nikad nisam izgubila nadu.

2442
02:03:11,000 --> 02:03:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja imam takvu vjeru da mi je Bog blizu.

2443
02:03:15,000 --> 02:03:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam nazad pet godina imala izljev u plućima.

2444
02:03:20,000 --> 02:03:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] I napad na srcu.

2445
02:03:23,000 --> 02:03:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Po noći mi je došlo.

2446
02:03:25,000 --> 02:03:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam po danu radila normalno, u školi sam bila.

2447
02:03:29,000 --> 02:03:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Po noći kao da me nekog dario s nožem u prsa

2448
02:03:35,000 --> 02:03:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] i da me krvi ide.

2449
02:03:37,000 --> 02:03:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se probudim, pa nemam krvi.

2450
02:03:40,000 --> 02:03:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idem u banj, pogledam na špigler.

2451
02:03:43,000 --> 02:03:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nemam.

2452
02:03:44,000 --> 02:03:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ne mogu dihat.

2453
02:03:49,000 --> 02:03:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] pokucam predstavnici.

2454
02:03:51,000 --> 02:03:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je slabo i ja ne mogu dihat.

2455
02:03:53,000 --> 02:03:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Po i to sam takve doživjela.

2456
02:03:55,000 --> 02:03:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odvedu me u bolnicu.

2457
02:03:57,000 --> 02:03:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Izljev, pluća.

2458
02:03:59,000 --> 02:04:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Napad srca.

2459
02:04:02,000 --> 02:04:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Misli su ja sam gotova.

2460
02:04:07,000 --> 02:04:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] jednu noć, bila sam više tamo nego vamo.

2461
02:04:10,000 --> 02:04:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja po noći sanjam da sam ja kao, kao prekla,

2462
02:04:14,000 --> 02:04:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] kao jedna glista.

2463
02:04:17,000 --> 02:04:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Od mene nema ništa, ali ja osjećam da je Isus kod mene.

2464
02:04:25,000 --> 02:04:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] da me on čuva.

2465
02:04:27,000 --> 02:04:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kažem pomoze mi.

2466
02:04:28,000 --> 02:04:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sama sam.

2467
02:04:29,000 --> 02:04:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam prebrodila to.

2468
02:04:34,000 --> 02:04:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja ne uzimam nikakve lijekova.

2469
02:04:36,000 --> 02:04:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene liječnici pita:

2470
02:04:38,000 --> 02:04:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Kakve lijekova uzmeš?"

2471
02:04:39,000 --> 02:04:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja uzimam nikakve.

2472
02:04:41,000 --> 02:04:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam uzmem ta kipirina,

2473
02:04:43,000 --> 02:04:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] ako mi velika vršina dođe.

2474
02:04:45,000 --> 02:04:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kako možeš tako?

2475
02:04:47,000 --> 02:04:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imala sam već 80 godina prešla.

2476
02:04:50,000 --> 02:04:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kako?

2477
02:04:52,000 --> 02:04:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja nemam po problema.

2478
02:04:54,000 --> 02:04:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema potrebe.

2479
02:04:56,000 --> 02:04:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nema potrebe.

2480
02:04:57,000 --> 02:04:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su ipak pronašli

2481
02:04:59,000 --> 02:05:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] neku penicelinu vrste tako da su me izvukli iz toga.

2482
02:05:04,000 --> 02:05:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali imam sada recimo poteškoća dihanja

2483
02:05:08,000 --> 02:05:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] i glas mi se mijenja.

2484
02:05:10,000 --> 02:05:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Više puta ne mogu govoriti jasno.

2485
02:05:14,000 --> 02:05:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Više puta me je muram.

2486
02:05:16,000 --> 02:05:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer imam takozvanu

2487
02:05:19,000 --> 02:05:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] azma bronchiale.

2488
02:05:24,000 --> 02:05:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to dođe voda s godinama.

2489
02:05:28,000 --> 02:05:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zato trebaš prihvat ono što dođe.

2490
02:05:31,000 --> 02:05:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažeš i svoj pomozi mi.

2491
02:05:32,000 --> 02:05:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ako je već vrijeme onda uz njima što je mogu.

2492
02:05:35,000 --> 02:05:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Još vas Bog ovdje treba oći to.

2493
02:05:40,000 --> 02:05:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bližimo se kraju našeg intervjua.

2494
02:05:46,000 --> 02:05:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Htio sam vas pitat još par stvari.

2495
02:05:48,000 --> 02:05:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prva, kad ste se prvi put vratili u Grahovo i kakav je osjećaj bio vratica?

2496
02:05:53,000 --> 02:05:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se vratila prvi put 81. godine.

2497
02:05:58,000 --> 02:06:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moja veća braća bila još živa u Zagrebu.

2498
02:06:01,000 --> 02:06:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja njima kažem ja imam želju vidjeti Grahovo jer ja sam bila mala ja ne znam kako izgleda.

2499
02:06:07,000 --> 02:06:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo pameti neke po, dakle, jednu dolinu i nešto.

2500
02:06:12,000 --> 02:06:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bih htjela vidjeti.

2501
02:06:15,000 --> 02:06:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Neidi, kažem, ubićete Srbi.

2502
02:06:17,000 --> 02:06:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ma ko će mi ubiti Srbi?

2503
02:06:19,000 --> 02:06:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imam talijansko državljanstvo.

2504
02:06:20,000 --> 02:06:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam redovnica, idem kao redovnica.

2505
02:06:22,000 --> 02:06:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam uvijek išla kao redovnica.

2506
02:06:24,000 --> 02:06:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se ne skidam.

2507
02:06:26,000 --> 02:06:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam redovnica i ako me hoće ubiti kao redovnicu nek me ubiju.

2508
02:06:30,000 --> 02:06:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja sam redovnica.

2509
02:06:32,000 --> 02:06:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne skidam sa sebe ništa.

2510
02:06:34,000 --> 02:06:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek u drugom odijelu ja sam to izabrala.

2511
02:06:37,000 --> 02:06:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog me ne htio, ja sam to izabrala.

2512
02:06:39,000 --> 02:06:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idem ja.

2513
02:06:41,000 --> 02:06:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Išla sam u Kiseljak.

2514
02:06:44,000 --> 02:06:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] išla u Livno.

2515
02:06:46,000 --> 02:06:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo sam ocijela kod časnice stara Milostrnica.

2516
02:06:49,000 --> 02:06:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] I zamolila sam ako ima ko da me odvede u Grahovo.

2517
02:06:53,000 --> 02:06:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] I bio je župnik.

2518
02:06:55,000 --> 02:06:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Župnik...

2519
02:06:57,000 --> 02:06:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Od kaže: "Ja ću ti odvesti."

2520
02:06:59,000 --> 02:07:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] I jedna časna sestra Milostrnica.

2521
02:07:02,000 --> 02:07:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ću ići s tobom.

2522
02:07:04,000 --> 02:07:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ona je u civilu. Ja sam kao redovnica, njih dvoje su u civilu.

2523
02:07:08,000 --> 02:07:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] I oni mene odvedu u Grahovo.

2524
02:07:13,000 --> 02:07:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Crkva narušena.

2525
02:07:15,000 --> 02:07:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije otvoren, bila zatvorena.

2526
02:07:19,000 --> 02:07:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Neka vrata su bile priključena.

2527
02:07:21,000 --> 02:07:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda pitam ko ima ključ.

2528
02:07:23,000 --> 02:07:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ima ključ jedan naš.

2529
02:07:25,000 --> 02:07:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Isto naš koji je blizu nas stanovao.

2530
02:07:28,000 --> 02:07:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan Filip Sarić.

2531
02:07:31,000 --> 02:07:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] O ženi on je sa pravoslovnom ženom.

2532
02:07:34,000 --> 02:07:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja pitam da li on mi otvorio crkvu.

2533
02:07:37,000 --> 02:07:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Unutra ništa.

2534
02:07:39,000 --> 02:07:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prljavo.

2535
02:07:41,000 --> 02:07:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Smeće je svoje.

2536
02:07:44,000 --> 02:07:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] došlo tako.

2537
02:07:45,000 --> 02:07:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sa plać.

2538
02:07:46,000 --> 02:07:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] A sam se svladala.

2539
02:07:50,000 --> 02:07:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam toga.

2540
02:07:51,000 --> 02:07:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad idem na groblje.

2541
02:07:53,000 --> 02:07:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Groblje je razrušeno.

2542
02:07:57,000 --> 02:07:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] jednog spomenika.

2543
02:07:58,000 --> 02:08:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je jedan bijeli spomenik.

2544
02:08:01,000 --> 02:08:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da li je bila, pisala gole, Andri.

2545
02:08:03,000 --> 02:08:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer moj bratić od moga strica, sin,

2546
02:08:07,000 --> 02:08:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] imao je osamnaest godina kad je umro od sušice.

2547
02:08:12,000 --> 02:08:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je mu bijeli bramorni spomenik.

2548
02:08:15,000 --> 02:08:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je nešto narušeno.

2549
02:08:17,000 --> 02:08:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da li je njegov bio ili nije.

2550
02:08:19,000 --> 02:08:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan drugi je bila samo Vulić Marija.

2551
02:08:24,000 --> 02:08:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moja baka bila Vulić Marija.

2552
02:08:26,000 --> 02:08:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čiji je bio ne znam.

2553
02:08:28,000 --> 02:08:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve srušeno.

2554
02:08:30,000 --> 02:08:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako mi je došlo na plać.

2555
02:08:33,000 --> 02:08:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo sam zaplakala.

2556
02:08:35,000 --> 02:08:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da ja ne mogu vidjeti ni ti grobova mojih djedova.

2557
02:08:42,000 --> 02:08:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Stvarno mi je tako bilo teško.

2558
02:08:45,000 --> 02:08:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sam se sladala.

2559
02:08:47,000 --> 02:08:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] U blizini su bile male kućice.

2560
02:08:50,000 --> 02:08:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nekoje naše žene su bile Hrvatice.

2561
02:08:53,000 --> 02:08:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna žena mene pita, jedna starica.

2562
02:08:56,000 --> 02:09:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene je hladno, a bilo je skoro u sedmom mjesecu.

2563
02:09:00,000 --> 02:09:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja sam bilo ovako lagano obučena.

2564
02:09:03,000 --> 02:09:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene je hladno jer graho je hladno, visina je.

2565
02:09:06,000 --> 02:09:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene je hladno jer držemo od hladnoće.

2566
02:09:10,000 --> 02:09:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ona mene kaže: "Sinko, tebi je hladno?"

2567
02:09:13,000 --> 02:09:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Je." "Pa čija si ti?"

2568
02:09:15,000 --> 02:09:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ja sam Kovačeva."

2569
02:09:17,000 --> 02:09:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Aaa, ti si naša."

2570
02:09:19,000 --> 02:09:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prepoznavali smo moga oca.

2571
02:09:21,000 --> 02:09:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam, kažem, izolja Sarić, od mije Kovača.

2572
02:09:26,000 --> 02:09:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ti ona mene uvede u svoju kućicu i dadne mi čašicu rakije.

2573
02:09:32,000 --> 02:09:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ispijem tu rakiju i ugrijem se.

2574
02:09:36,000 --> 02:09:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kažem, inače, ja ne pijem.

2575
02:09:41,000 --> 02:09:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali tad je bilo potrebno.

2576
02:09:43,000 --> 02:09:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako mi je bilo hladno.

2577
02:09:45,000 --> 02:09:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se tresla u hladnoće.

2578
02:09:47,000 --> 02:09:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda sam ispričala, imala sam samo sa sobom

2579
02:09:54,000 --> 02:09:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] malo bombona.

2580
02:09:58,000 --> 02:10:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] I vidla sam malih spava.

2581
02:10:02,000 --> 02:10:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda sam njemu ostavila te bombone što sam imala da uhtašni.

2582
02:10:08,000 --> 02:10:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] drugo ništa. Nisam imala sa sobom.

2583
02:10:10,000 --> 02:10:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su me odveli oni u knin.

2584
02:10:13,000 --> 02:10:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] U kninu sam ocijela kod naših sestara.

2585
02:10:16,000 --> 02:10:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je tamo imali u bolnici, suradile.

2586
02:10:19,000 --> 02:10:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kod njih sam ostavila.

2587
02:10:21,000 --> 02:10:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam imala visoku vrućinu.

2588
02:10:24,000 --> 02:10:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Albo zamolila sam sestru, nisam rekla da imam vrućinu,

2589
02:10:28,000 --> 02:10:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] samo da mi dadne jednu čašu.

2590
02:10:31,000 --> 02:10:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne vode, nego čaja.

2591
02:10:43,000 --> 02:10:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jednu čašu čaja, toplega čaja da mi dadne.

2592
02:10:47,000 --> 02:10:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] To me voda zagrijalo i prošla mi je vrućina.

2593
02:10:51,000 --> 02:10:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda sam otišla u promjenu.

2594
02:10:55,000 --> 02:10:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moja baka, mamina mama, je iz promjene.

2595
02:11:00,000 --> 02:11:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je bila Validžić iz promjene.

2596
02:11:02,000 --> 02:11:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja sam upoznala od svećenika Mirko Validžić.

2597
02:11:09,000 --> 02:11:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ga sam upoznala u Zagrebu.

2598
02:11:12,000 --> 02:11:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moji preci su iz promjene otišli u Liskovicu.

2599
02:11:17,000 --> 02:11:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] A, vidite.

2600
02:11:19,000 --> 02:11:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moja baka, inače i naši su od tih kraja.

2601
02:11:22,000 --> 02:11:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moja baka je bila iz promjene.

2602
02:11:25,000 --> 02:11:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam htjela vidjeti gdje je ona rođena.

2603
02:11:29,000 --> 02:11:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tamo je Mirko čekao, taj Mirko Validžić svećenik.

2604
02:11:34,000 --> 02:11:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je mene čekao i on nam pokazao sve.

2605
02:11:37,000 --> 02:11:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa smo išli i na Visovac.

2606
02:11:40,000 --> 02:11:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sam ja prebrodila i vrućinu u sve toj stvari.

2607
02:11:43,000 --> 02:11:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve.

2608
02:11:45,000 --> 02:11:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] A zadnji put, a prvi put da sam nakon toliko godina spavala u Grahovo.

2609
02:11:53,000 --> 02:11:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo kad je imali smo blagoslov.

2610
02:11:56,000 --> 02:11:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je za sve to Kiliju.

2611
02:11:59,000 --> 02:12:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad se ne sjećam se koje godine to je bilo.

2612
02:12:02,000 --> 02:12:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda sam ja otišla u Grahovo.

2613
02:12:06,000 --> 02:12:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] da i kod naših tih Sarića koji od peša, kod klek Krešimira.

2614
02:12:15,000 --> 02:12:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Krešimira Sarića je kod njegove mame, kod njih sam spavala.

2615
02:12:21,000 --> 02:12:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] njegov brat, Darin, ko je zove.

2616
02:12:24,000 --> 02:12:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, teto, oni su mene zvali teto.

2617
02:12:28,000 --> 02:12:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam ja njih dosta pomagala kad su izbjegli u Livnu.

2618
02:12:32,000 --> 02:12:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene su iz Zagreba javili.

2619
02:12:35,000 --> 02:12:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, nekoji su graholjeni izbjegli u Livnu, nemaju ništa.

2620
02:12:39,000 --> 02:12:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja sam bila tada u, dakle, u Askoli, Pičeno.

2621
02:12:43,000 --> 02:12:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imali smo prigode da im šaljimo.

2622
02:12:46,000 --> 02:12:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam njima slala novac,

2623
02:12:49,000 --> 02:12:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] tako da su se pomogli, da su došli k sebi.

2624
02:12:52,000 --> 02:12:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tako onda oni mene zovu teta Celina.

2625
02:12:55,000 --> 02:13:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda kaže, ja sam ti napravio krevet u svojoj sobi.

2626
02:13:01,000 --> 02:13:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Drag, hvala ti, kaže.

2627
02:13:03,000 --> 02:13:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja dugo nisam zaspala.

2628
02:13:05,000 --> 02:13:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čula sam sve životinice, kaže, po noći.

2629
02:13:10,000 --> 02:13:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to je meni tako, Bože, dragi, kako je to, kažem lijepo.

2630
02:13:14,000 --> 02:13:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja inače volim životinicom.

2631
02:13:17,000 --> 02:13:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bože, kako je to, kažem lijepo, šta su od nas napravili.

2632
02:13:20,000 --> 02:13:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kuda smo se morali potucat po svijetu, od mila do nedraga.

2633
02:13:26,000 --> 02:13:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] A eto, ja nakon toliko godina ipak sam došla u taj kraj kojeg sam žela.

2634
02:13:32,000 --> 02:13:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja volim taj kraj, interesantno.

2635
02:13:35,000 --> 02:13:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je vaš rodni kraj?

2636
02:13:36,000 --> 02:13:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je moj rodni kraj i moja braća to nisu mogla pojmiti.

2637
02:13:40,000 --> 02:13:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da ja idem tako, tako daleko jer ipak sam bila malena.

2638
02:13:44,000 --> 02:13:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znam sve to, ne poznajem niti ljudi, niti toliko sela, ništa.

2639
02:13:49,000 --> 02:13:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja poznam samo to naše selo, ništa drugo.

2640
02:13:53,000 --> 02:13:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kažem, ja to volim.

2641
02:13:55,000 --> 02:14:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] I znate što, osobito zadnji put kad sam bila jer je bilo već uzorano sve polje.

2642
02:14:01,000 --> 02:14:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ti Brežulci su tako mili.

2643
02:14:04,000 --> 02:14:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pitomi.

2644
02:14:05,000 --> 02:14:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako pitomi su.

2645
02:14:07,000 --> 02:14:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to je se meni ostalo, kaže, pa Bože, to je stvarno jedan lijep kraj.

2646
02:14:12,000 --> 02:14:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je prekrasan kraj.

2647
02:14:14,000 --> 02:14:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] I s to se mene tako dojmilo.

2648
02:14:16,000 --> 02:14:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kažem, pa ipak moji roditelji, moji djedo i bak i pradjede koji su tu došli.

2649
02:14:23,000 --> 02:14:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerojatno su, to se njima dopalo.

2650
02:14:25,000 --> 02:14:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tu su mogli živjeti, imat svoje blago, imat svoju zemlju i raditi pošteno i živjeti pošteno u Bože milosti.

2651
02:14:34,000 --> 02:14:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

2652
02:14:36,000 --> 02:14:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste li, vaši predsi su živjeli tamo u lijepom skladnom životu i određeni ljudi su to prekinuli.

2653
02:14:48,000 --> 02:14:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste uspili oprostiti onima koji su vas otirali iz grafova?

2654
02:14:52,000 --> 02:14:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znate, ja kažem, ja naravno, ja sam zahvalna mnogim Srbima koji su nas spasili.

2655
02:14:59,000 --> 02:15:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer su bili ipak pošteni ljudi i pravedni.

2656
02:15:03,000 --> 02:15:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kažem, to moram priznat, ja bi to priznala pred svakim, jer ja sam to proživjela.

2657
02:15:08,000 --> 02:15:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Osobito koji su bili u našom selu i koji su bili poznanci moga oca.

2658
02:15:14,000 --> 02:15:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je ljudi koji su bili zli. A ja mislim da su došli iz drugih krajeva koji su se htjeli osvećivati.

2659
02:15:20,000 --> 02:15:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog zna zašto. Pa su se osvećivali na nevinim ljudima.

2660
02:15:24,000 --> 02:15:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kažem, vjerojatno su bili u neznanju, dakle, u mržnji.

2661
02:15:32,000 --> 02:15:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možda biti, jer kad su izgubili svoju državu, onda bili su prerareženi.

2662
02:15:39,000 --> 02:15:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu znali same šta hoće.

2663
02:15:44,000 --> 02:15:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zato kažem, treba im oprostiti, ja opraštam svima.

2664
02:15:48,000 --> 02:15:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovdje su dolazili, baš iz Beograda,

2665
02:15:54,000 --> 02:15:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] jedan profesor imao je problema sa zdravljem.

2666
02:15:58,000 --> 02:16:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam njega vodila, plaćila mu put za tramaj.

2667
02:16:01,000 --> 02:16:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vodila ga sam na Fiumičino, praoslavac je bi.

2668
02:16:05,000 --> 02:16:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa čovjek njega treba pomoć, on je u bolesti.

2669
02:16:09,000 --> 02:16:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] I mi smo imali u školi isto par Srba.

2670
02:16:12,000 --> 02:16:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo ih imali gratis, bezpasleno u školi.

2671
02:16:17,000 --> 02:16:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, i bili su oni nama jako fini.

2672
02:16:20,000 --> 02:16:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je jedan profesor sa dvoje djece,

2673
02:16:22,000 --> 02:16:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji je radio na ambasadi.

2674
02:16:25,000 --> 02:16:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, isto je imao djete, bio kod nas u zabavištu.

2675
02:16:28,000 --> 02:16:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, mi smo gratis njemu dali.

2676
02:16:30,000 --> 02:16:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, slušajte, on nije kriv što su drugi to napravili.

2677
02:16:34,000 --> 02:16:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi ne smo ima sve staviti u isti koš.

2678
02:16:38,000 --> 02:16:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ima ljudi koji su pošteni, koji su radišni, koji se poštivaju druge.

2679
02:16:43,000 --> 02:16:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] A bilo je bivljaka, možda i među našim je bilo bivljaka.

2680
02:16:48,000 --> 02:16:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koji su nešto učinili što nisu trebali, kao kršćani, kao katolici.

2681
02:16:54,000 --> 02:16:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, ali treba oprostiti.

2682
02:16:57,000 --> 02:17:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mnogi ljudi su u neznanju, mnogi su bili možda razočarani.

2683
02:17:01,000 --> 02:17:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Izgubili su državu, izgubili sve i razočarani su.

2684
02:17:06,000 --> 02:17:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Iz toga razočaranja činili su nevolju.

2685
02:17:10,000 --> 02:17:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] A treba im oprostiti.

2686
02:17:12,000 --> 02:17:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dragi bok je otac sviju, i Hroata, i Srba, i Slovenaca.

2687
02:17:16,000 --> 02:17:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je jedini bok.

2688
02:17:20,000 --> 02:17:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] On sigurno nas sve voli, zato i mi moramo između sebe oprostiti, dakle nastojeti zaboraviti i ne prigovarati uvijek.

2689
02:17:31,000 --> 02:17:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Taj mi je tam prvi to, isto kao uvijek. On nam je u to prvi, treba što zaboraviti.

2690
02:17:36,000 --> 02:17:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo svi slabi, svi imamo naše pogreške, možemo pogrešiti, ali trebamo isto moliti oprostenje i trebamo oprostiti drugoma koji nas uvrijedili.

2691
02:17:48,000 --> 02:17:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je naš kršćanski život. Ako hoćemo lijepo živjeti, ako hoćemo u jednoj zajednici skladno živjeti, moramo jednim drugim opraštati.

2692
02:18:00,000 --> 02:18:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer svi smo mi grešni, svi mi pogrešimo. Niko od nas nije peo bez greha, iz pogrešaka.

2693
02:18:08,000 --> 02:18:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja uvijek kažem: "Ah, to sam pogrešila, vidi pa to." Priznam, jer zašto bi?

2694
02:18:13,000 --> 02:18:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imam pravo i pogrešiti jer sam čovjek.

2695
02:18:16,000 --> 02:18:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Osoba sam, imam svoji nedostataka, imam dobri strani, imam loših.

2696
02:18:23,000 --> 02:18:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Trebam prihvatiti jedne i druge.

2697
02:18:27,000 --> 02:18:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je. Za kraj, poroka mladima, posebno u Grahovo.

2698
02:18:32,000 --> 02:18:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja preporučujem svima da najpre imaju vjeru u Boga, ufanje u Boga.

2699
02:18:39,000 --> 02:18:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je naš Otac, sve nas ljubi i voli. I On će nam uvijek pomoći.

2700
02:18:45,000 --> 02:18:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] A trebamo imati i razumijevanje prema drugima.

2701
02:18:50,000 --> 02:18:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nemojmo osuđivati one koje nisu ništa učinili jer su nama drugi nešto učinili.

2702
02:18:57,000 --> 02:19:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] I misliti da oni su krivi. Ne, moramo to jako razlikovati.

2703
02:19:02,000 --> 02:19:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je ljudi koji su učini zla, a imam sada ljudi dobri koje trebaš prihvatiti, s njima živjeti kao ljudi.

2704
02:19:10,000 --> 02:19:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da se razumemo, da se poštivamo jedne i druge. Poštivamo njihovu narodnost, poštivamo i njihovu vjeru.

2705
02:19:18,000 --> 02:19:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni će poštivati našu narodnost i našu vjeru. Ako hoćemo živjeti kao ljudi, kao djeca Božja. Svi smo mi djeca Božja. To trebamo imati na pameti.

2706
02:19:31,000 --> 02:19:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja molim za sve naše ljude. Svi oni koji su u grahu, i praoslavci i katolici, da žive u slozi, u razumijevanju.

2707
02:19:42,000 --> 02:19:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer nema drugoga nego. Trebamo jedne i druge poštivati, jedne i druge razumijeti, jedne i druge oprostiti.

2708
02:19:51,000 --> 02:19:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da tako možemo biti kao ljudi koji žive kao djeca Božja. Jer svi smo djeca Božja.

2709
02:19:59,000 --> 02:20:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] A Bog je samo jedan. Nije Bog ni srpski, ni hrvatski, ni slovenski, ni njemački.

2710
02:20:09,000 --> 02:20:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] I jedan za sve nas. Samo mi se dijelimo. Mi smo ograničeni.

2711
02:20:14,000 --> 02:20:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da. Sestra, hvala vam puno na ovo izvojenom vremenu.

2712
02:20:20,000 --> 02:20:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znate što, možda sam previše govorila koji put sam se zapila.

2713
02:20:24,000 --> 02:20:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ja talijansi govorim najviše. I onda koji put Hrvatski mi ne dođe rijet.

2714
02:20:30,000 --> 02:20:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nikakav problem. Meni je jako drago što ste nas primili.

2715
02:20:36,000 --> 02:20:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala što ste poživjeli. Dovoljno da se upoznamo i da svoju priču podijelite s nama.

2716
02:20:40,000 --> 02:20:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja pozdravljam sve dečke, sve mladeži.

2717
02:20:45,000 --> 02:20:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Drago ga Boga, prije svega, naka nam Bog bude uvek s nama, a da ljube i svoju domovinu, svoju obitelj i poštivaju i oca i majku i braću i sestru.

2718
02:20:57,000 --> 02:20:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

2719
02:20:58,000 --> 02:20:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

2720
02:20:59,000 --> 02:21:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo se za kraj možda pomoliti.

2721
02:21:00,000 --> 02:21:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zahvaljamo ti sve mogući Bože za sve tvoje dobrote koje si nam podijeli u našem životu.

2722
02:21:07,000 --> 02:21:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Molimo te slava Otcu i sinu i duhu svetom kako bijaše na početku, kako i sada i vazda i u vijeke vijekova. Amen.

2723
02:21:17,000 --> 02:21:19,139
[SPEAKER_01] oca i sine i duha svetog.

2724
02:21:19,139 --> 02:21:19,760
[SPEAKER_01] Amen.

